(6, 10, 1, '6_s.jpg', 'Sergio Mega', '', '<p>Sergio Mega - DJ, producer, musician, one of the pioneers in Ukrainian electronic dance music. In the early 80&rsquo;s he began studying music at the Kiev Conservatory, his DJ-career began in the mid 90&rsquo;s under the name DJ Megabeat. In 2004 he has founded his own label CTS records. Today, more than 50 releases by Sergio Mega are available on CD, vinyl, and in digital format around the world. <br />\r\nSince 2008 Sergio Mega becomes a part of Afro Acid family. Sergio Mega and CTS Records every year present Ukraine at the international festivals of electronic music, and work in close collaboration with musicians and record labels from different countries. This experience makes possible to keep up with the latest trends and technology development areas of electronic dance music. Ukrainian artist has experience of International Dance Music Awards Official Afterparty in Miami, Dance Parade in Rotterdam, the sets in cult clubs of Amsterdam, dance floors of Goa, Jazz Koktebel Fest, and Kazantip of course.&nbsp;<br />\r\nSince&nbsp; 2009 Sergio has been a lecturer of the National Academy of Culture and Arts Managing personnel. Subject: Composition and Computer arrangement.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/sergio.mega.cts\"> FACEBOOK</a><br />\r\n<a href=\"http://soundcloud.com/sergio-mega\">SOUNDCLOUD</a><br />\r\n<a href=\"http://sergiomega.com\">www.sergiomega.com</a>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', '', '2016-08-01 14:35:31', '2016-08-01 14:35:31'),
(12, 6, 1, '12_s.jpg', 'Tiesel', '', 'Serge Tovstoloozky aka TSL aka Tiesel aka Yehuanah (1970 - 2007). At the end of 80-ies played in punk and new wave groups, was keen on computers. At the beginning of 90-ies was a member of working group of Ministry of culture by supporting information to libraries in Ukraine. In the middle of 90-ies presented as DJ Yehuanah and consisting of the project Clouds Generator, was keen on algorithmic composition. At the end of 90-ies worked as studio equipment adviser and sound engineer. In 2001 produced the album &quot;Model&quot; of the group &quot;Ocean Elsy&quot; whereupon produced a lot of works of Ukrainian and Russian artists. Since 2003 - managing director of rspf.cc - sound studio, which clients are the leading Ukrainian and Russian artists and labels.<br />\r\nIn 2006 Tiesel become a foothold member of CTS records team. www.rspf.cc<br />\r\n&nbsp;', 'Информация будет доступна позже...', '2016-05-16 13:46:34', '2016-05-16 13:46:34'),
(13, 12, 1, '13_s.jpg', 'Sambooca', '', 'Sambooca is - Korovin and Dj Fresh from St.Petersburg (Russia). They first met at radio station and finally teamed up in the studio in early 2006. Each of participants by that moment already had wide experience of work in musical sphere.<br />\r\nDJ Fresh started his musical career in 1997 as a DJ for various night clubs and major Raves. His outstanding gigs, unique musical style and naturally charming personality attracted many famous club promoters right away and made him one of the headliners for biggest dance events, such as DJ Parade, Kazantip and Vostochny Udar (Eastern Attack). While performing on different stages in Russia and abroad and playing at numerous fashion shows and parties, DJ Fresh meets many famous artists (musicians): Benny Benassi(Italy), DJ SASH(Germany), DJ Marcus Wallic (London UK), DJ Martin(Manchester UK), DJ Nick Hodgkins (Leeds UK), Fluke project (London UK), Richard Thair (Warp Records, UK), Dublex Inc.(Germany), DJ Zebra(Finland), David Penn(Spain), DJ Ravin(Buddha Bar, France), David Vendetta(Paris, France)&hellip; In November 2003, DJ Fresh was nominated for prestigious international award at &quot;Movida Corona DJ\'s Competition&quot;. Currently DJ Fresh has residency in two glamorous clubs located in the heart of St-Petersburg - &quot;Led Lemon&quot; and &quot;Buddha Bar Spb&quot;.<br />\r\nKorovin\'s musical career begins in 1997, as he start to play as a DJ for one of the biggest clubs in St.-Petersburg. At the same time he works at sound recording studio SKY as a sound engineer, where he meets singer and musician Nikita. In the same year they produce the first album and the single &quot;Uleteli navsegda&quot; which hits like a bomb and gets the first places on russian music channels MTV Russia, MUZTV and all leading radio stations. Since 2003 Korovin looks for a record label, who could be interested to release his tracks outside of Russia. Long-term work in production studio of leading russian radio stations Russian Radio, Dinamit FM and radio Maximum helps him to get in contact with well known Russian DJs and musicians such as DJ Kosinus, DJ Sludkey, DJ Slon, Pimenov, DJ Tsvetkoff, DJ Dansky, DJ Fresh, DJ Majestic and many others. He successfully cooperates with the whole galaxy of such talented people as Moussa Clarke (Oven Ready, UK), Keith Thompson (Wakingmonster records, US), Funky junction (Votu, IT), David Vendetta (RadioFg, FR) and SergioMega (CTS.UA). <br />', 'Информация будет доступна позже...', '2016-08-01 14:32:47', '2016-08-01 14:32:47'),
