(17, 34, 1, '17_s.jpg', 'Ikiro', '', 'CTS records presents new project &ndash; Ikiro. Ikiro is a project of progressive electronic music, which structure for now includes 1 producer: Sergey Ikiro and 1 singer Vanda Li Li. They can easily encompass several styles, ranging from deep and progressive to idm-relax and ambient-lounge. Ikiro-is a japaniese name, which means-&ldquo;be alive&rdquo;, but from the ancient manuscriptes Ikiro also means &ndash; &ldquo;heart&rdquo;&amp;&ldquo;flower&rdquo;. Serge has started his musician way on the small french label &ldquo;Webmusic&rdquo;. He have been producing hardcore, dnb, techno, trance, eurodance for this label for 2 years. In 2003 and 2004 Ikiro took part in the RFIelektromusic award which took place in Paris, judges was chaired by Laurent Garnier, in 2004 Ikiro took the 4th place. Ikiro- music impresses the listeners by its original perception, retaining funky overtones, splattered with plenty of surprises and laced with euphoric uplifting moments. At present time Serge Ikiro can be found busy in the studio working on new releases. And already took place in &lsquo;&rsquo;TenDance&rsquo;&rsquo;-10 the best dance tracks in Ukraine.<br />\r\nIkiro will continue his work together with professional singer Vanda Li Li about new releases and already in near future plan to finish an electronic music album with CTS records, which will include the best tunes.', 'Информация будет доступна позже...', '2016-08-01 13:22:51', '2016-08-01 13:22:51'),
