(19, 39, 1, '19_s.jpg', 'Ekspert', 'https://www.facebook.com/Ekspertiza', '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">DJ EKSPERT &ndash; is CTS Records label resident, he is staff DJ of legendary Ukrainian band &ndash; Green Grey, he is the musician who always takes part in Gorchitza Live Project concerts and co-works with rap group &ndash; The New Union.<br />\r\nNow DJ Ekspert takes an active part in creating the brand new Green Grey album. In 2008 he won the audience and the jury of the famous international scratch festival DMC in Kiev, having entered Top-10 winners of the festival.<br />\r\nTracks by DJ Ekspert steadily enter Ukrainian and foreign musical charts. As a talented sound producer, he works in genres from Downtempo and Hip Hop to Electro &amp; Techno.</div>', '', '2016-07-29 13:55:11', '2016-07-29 13:55:11'),
(20, 40, 1, '20_s.jpg', 'D-mond', '', 'Jose Drummond aka DJ D\'mond did his first solo Painting exhibition in 1989. In the same year his passion behind the decks exploded becoming resident of the legendary Lisbon warehouse parties and some of the trendy city clubs.<br />\r\nIn 1994 his curiosity for Chinese art made him fly to Asia. His record collection was his luggage. The adventure was only about to start&hellip;<br />\r\nTen years later his devotion for electronic music recognized him as a key player in the development of Asian Club Scene, touring everywhere in big China. <br />\r\nHis level of exposure, enabled him to team up with some of the industry icons, including Sasha, John Digweed, Derrick May, Nick Warren, James Zabiela, Lee Burridge, Chris Fortier, Anthony Pappa, Goldie and DJ SS. <br />\r\nIn 2005 was 177 in the 250 DJ MAG Chart, repeating the list in the following year with number 186. In summer 2009 D\'mond is starting on CTS records with single &quot;Announcement&quot;.', '', '2016-07-29 13:55:22', '2016-07-29 13:55:22'),
(21, 45, 1, '21_s.jpg', 'DJ Derbastler', 'https://www.facebook.com/DJDERBASTLER', 'Was born in Kiev in 1972.<br />\r\nIn 1989 began to play in independent Kiev groups such as &quot;Elektryky&quot;, &quot;Yarn&quot;, &quot;Radiodelo&quot;, &quot;SHake Hi-Fi, etc. At that time his priorities in music were Minimal, Noise, indie-tehno, experimental music, alternative guitar music. Became a sound producer of many albums.<br />\r\nIn1994 was included into the group &quot;Foa-Hoka&quot; and became its participant and co-producer. Since that year does work as DJ. Is an initiator and co-organizer of the first techno- and rave-parties in Ukraine.<br />\r\nIn1995-98 musical director of &quot;Torba Entertainment&quot;. As DJ plays in the clubs, open-air parties with the audience about 70 000 of people. Takes part in promo actions of the companies Coca Cola, Lucky Strike, West, LM, Reebok and many native brands.<br />\r\nIn1998 together with Vitaly Bardetsky published the first CD of the Ukrainian underground - &quot;Who is next?&quot; At the same 98th year together with K. Procenko began the multimedia art project &quot;Radio Eurasia&quot; which became unique on the Ukrainian stage. With this project musicians have traveled through Ukraine and a part of the Europe - France, Venice and many other countries.<br />\r\nIn 2000 in the Cinema house created &quot;life&quot; set to &quot;Dumb&quot; film. It was unexampled event for Ukraine. It\'s main point was that DJs during the review of the film selected a music by the film extemporaneously.<br />\r\nIn 2001 was a participant of the international media project &quot;Dream Game&quot; in Kiev on the &quot;Dynamo&quot; stadium.<br />\r\nFrom 2000 to 2002 was a musical adviser of the Kiev International Media-Art Festival (KIMAF)<br />\r\nIn 2002 was a resident of the gallery &quot;Rebel Minds&quot; in Berlin.<br />\r\nIn 2003 together with K. Procenko was founded the label &quot;Thermos records&quot; on which had published CD named &quot;Music for lorry drivers&quot;. Was a participant of the international festival &quot;New Sound&quot; in Kiev. Performance was on a biennale in Venice.<br />\r\nIn 2004 was playing in Vienna on the symposium &quot;Vienna grand art academy&quot;.<br />\r\nIn 2006 DJ Derbastler was signed to CTS records.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDJ Derbastler - is a permanent participant of the festival &quot;Fashion seasons&quot;. In that year became a laureate of the premium for the best sound track of &quot;Fashion seasons&quot;. Since 1997 and till today is a musical designer of radio, television and night clubs. Played literally in all clubs in Kiev. <br />', '', '2016-07-28 14:13:09', '2016-07-28 14:13:09'),
(23, 24, 1, '23_s.jpg', 'Niels von Geyer', '', 'DJ Niels von Geyer, Berlin, plays a mixture of progressivehouse, pumpinhouse, vocalhouse, and classix, trance, electro. Ows a studio in Berlin together with his partner Mattias Harnos. As a dance music producer, his projects are Clubmossphere, Brotherhood of Sound, Disco Hools &amp; NVG. DJ Niels von Geyer works in Hamburg, Berlin and Moscow International publications and places in different dancecharts, mixed compilation THE ANNUAL for Ministry of Sound track at CLUBBERSGUIDE TO BERLIN (Ministry of Sound)&hellip;Remix Kate Ryan &hellip;Snap. He is signed to labels of Berlin-Phenomena, Clubmossphere, Germany, CTS (UA). Participates in different venues of Germany, Europe and worldwide - Loveparade, Lovestern Galactica, DJ-Meeting, Big Bang (Sweden), etc. In his non DJ-Life he is engaged in Extravadance - Radioshow at NRJ, Weiss der Geyer radio show, Eurotops, Dancehouse, Power Vision at the central German TV (ARD/ZDF). Also known as an actor (ZDF - serial &quot;During the next maneuver ...&quot;), free author for TV (LoopTV at Viva cannel), music journalist (Dates &amp; Tendance), music editor - [030] Berlin, DJ Promotion for Ministry of Sound (Germany), Kosmo, Great Stuff Recordings, Clubland, Sony /BMG.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMore information at following websites:<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/nielsvongeyer\">FACEBOOK</a><br />\r\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.clubmossphere.de/\">www.clubmossphere.de</a><br />\r\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.berlin-phenomena.de/\">www.berlin-phenomena.de</a><br />\r\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.djpoolmos.clubmossphere.de/\">www.djpoolmos.clubmossphere.de</a><br />\r\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.ministryofsound.de/\">www.ministryofsound.de</a><br />\r\n<br />', 'Niels von Geyer (Berlin) работает в миксе из&nbsp; стилей&nbsp;House / Minimal/ new Electro<br />\r\n<br />\r\nДеятельность продюсера:<br />\r\nСобственная студия в Берлине с партнером Матце Ангел. Продюсирование dancemusic Clubmossphere, Brotherhood of Sound, Нильс фон Гайер, Disco Hools &amp; NVG.Работа в качестве продюсера в Гамбурге, Берлине, Москве. Международные публикации и лидирующие позиции в различных dancecharts, микс-сборник The Annaul для Ministry Of Sound, Soundtrack на Clubbersguide To Berlin (Ministry Of Sound). Label: Berlin-Phenomena, Clubmossphere Germany Выступления: Loveparade, Locestern Galactica, DJ-Meeting, Big Bang (Швеция), различные клубы Германии, Европы.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNon DJ-Life: <br />\r\nГлавный редактор и ведущий &quot;Ministry Of Sound Radio&quot; Германия<br />\r\nДиректор Promotion Company Clubmossphere Germany<br />\r\naктер, радио- и теле- ведущий, фотограф<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDJ Promotion www.clubmossphere.net  для Ministry Of Sound, Kosmo, Great Stuff, Clubland, SonyBmg, MUTE, EMI, Urbanheat Recordings<br />\r\nСреди заказчиков:<br />\r\nIda Corr &amp; Fedde Le Grand, Samim, David Guetta, Booty Luv, Bob Sinclar, Eric Prydz, Moby, Robbie Williams, IIO, Alex Gaudino, Tomcraft, Hooligan, Mason, David Guetta, Deep Dish, Stonebridge, Therese, Asbo, Mousse T., Erasure, Simply Red, Snap, Laurent Wolf<br />\r\nЗолотые пластинки за: <br />\r\nEric Prydz &ndash; Call on me, Kate Ryan &ndash; Desenchante, Bob Sinclar &ndash; Lovegeneration, Ida Corr - Let me thing about it и другие.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/nielsvongeyer\">FACEBOOK</a><br />\r\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.clubmossphere.de/\">www.clubmossphere.de</a><br />\r\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.berlin-phenomena.de/\">www.berlin-phenomena.de</a><br />\r\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.djpoolmos.clubmossphere.de/\">www.djpoolmos.clubmossphere.de</a><br />\r\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.ministryofsound.de/\">www.ministryofsound.de</a>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br type=\"_moz\" />', '2016-08-01 13:49:14', '2016-08-01 13:49:14'),
(24, 5, 1, '24_s.jpg', 'Tka4', '', '<p>Tka4 aka Vasily Tkach.</p>\r\n<p>Famous Ukrainian songwrtter.</p>\r\n<p>Well known by his great production experience.</p>\r\n<p>Working with many pop music artists, TV channels, radio stations, music festivals,</p>\r\n<p>now have a credits at CTS records</p>\r\n<p>This days Tka4 making new sounds and&nbsp;traveling&nbsp;around the world.</p>', 'Информация будет доступна позже...', '2016-05-16 13:46:31', '2016-05-16 13:46:31'),
(25, 56, 1, '25_s.jpg', 'Aquabeat', 'https://www.facebook.com/Aquabeat-djs-264409667319', 'AQUABEAT<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAquabeat &ndash; is one of the best Ukrainian techno duos, who is presenting new, interesting, high-quality sound. Similar points of view on electronic music were resulted in creation of the joint project in 2007. Each of participants of duet has the unique style that does their joint works twice as stronger.<br />\r\nIn early 2007, Aquabeat seriously started writing their own material, and as a result was created first joint track - The Energy. During the first week, The Energy entered the top 10 sales at www.juno.co.uk, one of the largest Internet-shops of electronic music in the world, and soon took the third position.<br />\r\nSince then, career of Aquabeat duo began to develop with the breakneck speed.<br />\r\nTheir trademark sound is based on the Techno/Minimal, Tech - House/Electro waves. But they are not afraid to experiment with other electronic music styles, successfully combining them into one explosive cocktail, in which everybody can find something for yourself.<br />\r\nIn music stores all over the world, electronic music lovers can find more than 50 releases of Aquabeat duo. They are supported, playlisted and charted by many famous DJs around the world: Armin Van Buuren, John Aquaviva, Miles Dyson, Serge Devant, Ahmet Sendil, Andrea Bertolini, Piatto, Dandi &amp; Ugo, Phunk Investigation, Ricky Stone, George F, Dyno, AnGy KoRe, Glitter, Andrea Mattioli, Andrea Di Rocco, NHB, Daniele Petronelli, Fabrizio Pettorelli, Bismark &amp; more ...<br />\r\nSince 2008 - CTS Records label residents, since 2010 engaged in A&amp;R management in the CTS team.<br />\r\nAlso they work together with Italo Business Records, Bosphorus Underground Recordings, Plasmapool Media Entertainment, FHD Records, Flat Belly Records, Piso Records, Diva Records, Mystika Records, Clorophilla Records, No-Logik Records, Tracer Records, GF Recordings, The Source &amp; others&hellip;<br />\r\nBut Aquabeat won&rsquo;t stop their progress, they are preparing new releases, constantly improving their sound and looking for new approaches to writing music and performing it for the public.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nStay tuned...<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOfficial Web-site:<br />\r\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://myspace.com/aquabeatdjs\">www.myspace.com/aquabeatdjs</a><br />\r\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://cts-label.com\">www.cts-label.com</a><br />\r\n<br />', '', '2016-07-28 14:14:45', '2016-07-28 14:14:45'),
(26, 32, 1, '26_s.jpg', 'M.I.D.I.', '', 'Music has been the biggest passion in M.I.D.I.&rsquo;s life and he shares that passion with other people since the tender age of 13. In the early days of his career, in the Nineties, Vito Laforge aka Dj M.I.D.I. played records at disco shows in Puglia and in the neighbouring regions where he began developing his techniques and cultivating his style. In summer of 2001, M.I.D.I. ruled the &ldquo;Heaven Island Fashion Priv&eacute;&rdquo; at DNA in Taranto working together with J.T. Vannelli, Ivan Iacobucci, Leo Mas, Massimiliano Beca, Lenny Fontana, Deepswing and other international top names. Among other disco clubs he worked at Theorema in Metaponto, Green Park in Adelfia, Merendero in Casamassima, Pasilda in Taranto and Silver System in Brindisi. He has been signed as a resident dj for &quot;House Innovative&quot; a famous event organiser&rsquo;s directory covering the south of Italy. His first release, &quot;Beats and peaces&quot;, in 2002, in collaboration with Costantino &ldquo;Mixmaster&rdquo; Padovano for &quot;M.I.D.I. Mix and Soul&quot; project, marked the beginning of his career as producer. His career culminates in 2006 with the project &ldquo;NARCOX&rdquo; in collaboration with singer-producer-dj Mowree. Their first release &quot;Kiss me back&quot;, for Python Records marked their debut, followed by the mixes &quot;Low G Call E.p. 01&quot; for Sugarshake Reloaded Records and &quot;Burnin\'&quot; for Soundivision Records. Among the others they have had production credits on labels like MOLTO RECORDS, DEEP DEEN RECORDS, V.O.T.U. RECORDS and CTS records. M.I.D.I. has taken part in the major international music gigs such as the Winter Music Conference 2003 in Miami, together with Chus &amp; Cheballos, Funky Junction, Marcello Castelli and Dr Love, the Street Rave Parade 2004 in Bologna together with Jayculture team and Francesco Farfa, Stefano Greppi, Ralf, Bruno Bolla and many other colleagues. Finally M.I.D.I. has actively collaborated in radio transmissions such as &quot;Master Groove&quot; on Radio Company Puglia in 2002 and &quot;Mastermind&quot; on Radioerre in 2004. Actually he takes part in the transmission &ldquo;Set for dj&rsquo;s&rdquo; on Dub Radio (Miami).<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.djmidi.it/\" target=\"_blank\">www.djmidi.it</a><br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.myspace.com/mididj\">www.myspace.com/mididj</a>', 'Информация будет доступна позже...', '2016-08-01 13:30:47', '2016-08-01 13:30:47'),
(27, 30, 1, '27_s.jpg', 'Kotov & Andre Wilde', '', 'DJ Kotov and Andre Wilde exploded onto the DJing scene in 2001. Their love for music and thirst for success led them to their place as one of the top DJ duos on the Toronto scene. They quickly attracted a following audience and secured a favourite position with their impeccable talent and vivacious vibes.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWorking on the DJ scene and in LIVE projects with many well known artists. After big bang in The Guvernment club with famous Ferry Corsten, Kotov &amp; Andre Wilde makes cool performance together with Kaskade. Now is planned club project with resident of Super Star records &ndash; Tocadisco.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlaying in clubs of Montreal, Detroit, Miami, Chicago and New York as are Casa Blanca, The Docks, Cognac Lounge, The Guvernment, etc., Kotov &amp; Andre Wilde takes part in Electronic Music Open Air Festival in North America WEMF, Season 12. Now Kotov &amp; Andre Wilde makes their own sounds, run own club project &ldquo;VIP house&rdquo;, and have a credits at labels CTS records, Real Legacy records. They continue to bring us their scintillating music and extraordinary charisma while forging ahead onto new experiences.<br />', 'DJ Kotov и Andre Wilde ворвались на электронную сцену в 2001 году. Любовь к музыке и жажда успеха быстро утвердили их статус как одного из лучших DJ-дуэтов в Торонто. Они завоевали симпатии многих ценителей хорошей электронной музыки и заняли свою нишу среди канадских DJев благодаря таланту создавать живые, оригинальные ритмы.<br />\r\nВообще деятельность DJ Kotov и Andre Wilde иначе как бурной не назовешь. Они работали в сфере диджеинга и live-проектов со многими знаменитыми музыкантами.&nbsp; После взрывного выступления в клубе The Guvernment с Ferry Corsten создали бомбовый перформанс вместе с Kaskade, а так же совместного проект с резидентом Superstar recordings - Tocadisco в клубе Footwork.<br />\r\nДует постоянно играет в клубах Монреаля, Детройта, Майями, Чикаго и Нью-Йорка таких как: Casa Blanca, The Docks, Cognac Lounge, The Guvernment, в 2006 приняли приглашение участвовать в одном из самых знаменитых североамериканских Open Air - фестивалей WEMF (Session 12). На данный момент DJ Kotov и Andre Wilde активно создают новую музыку, работают над собственным клубным проектом \'VIP house\' и сотрудничают с лейблами Real Legacy records (USA), 4 Play Trax (Canada), Rawthentic (Canada), CTS records (Ukraine).<br />\r\nОни продолжают радовать нас своим искрометным битом и невероятной харизмой своих треков, никогда не останавливаясь на достигнутом в поисках новых музыкальных впечатлений!', '2016-08-01 13:38:25', '2016-08-01 13:38:25'),
(28, 29, 1, '28_s.jpg', 'MC Yug', '', '<div style=\"text-align: center;\">information coming soon</div>', 'Информация будет доступна позже...', '2016-08-01 13:41:33', '2016-08-01 13:41:33'),
(29, 7, 1, '29_s.jpg', 'Storm Tarrion', '', 'Storm Tarrion spawned from a troubled past growing up on the streets of Sydney Australia, you might say that his history led him to this point in time&hellip;. Music has always been a major part of his life, the most constant, it`s his driving passion. For the past ten years Adonaiiis has been writing heavily and composing original music in many forms. His style is unique and unlike any other, there are hints of rock, acid, electronic pop and old school house. The basis of his concept is to inspire the imagination and to make people listen a little closer, as there are many layers to his music. Storm understands that what is real and what is imagined is the same thing&hellip;.. After growing popularity, interest on the internet and some collaboration with other artists, now Storm already find a place to call home and to take things to a higher level - this is CTS records. <br />', 'Информация будет доступна позже...', '2016-08-01 13:52:46', '2016-08-01 13:52:46'),
