(830, 48, 1, '830_s.jpg', 'Dee Mares', 'https://www.facebook.com/chalyi', '<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Producer and graphic designer, Dee Mares looks at life through the prism of abstraction, saturating the world of interesting ideas, feelings and emotions. For several years, Dee was collecting all sorts of materials for the implementation of his new, creative ideas. <br />\r\nHis experiments with ambient, glitch and minimal eventually led to the creation of their own style - abstraction minimal, that distinguishes it from other producers.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Mares\' works inspire us to reflect and enter into a world where there are no standards and general rules, and where the sound of harmony flows on the covert of the brain and the heart beats in unison with minimalist beat.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Now Dee works with &quot;CTS Records&quot; and is a permanent resident in &quot;GUARANA Music Community&quot;.</span></p>', '', '2016-07-28 14:13:36', '2016-07-28 14:13:36'),
