(1335, 144, 'Voltereto & Doktor Alfred - Tinajo', 'CTS144113', '2011-06-09', '1335_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/tinajo/378154', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/tinajo/378154', 'Looking for powerful pick time tech-house? Here you are! Juicy beats are coming directly from Madrid, sunny Spain capital. Volteretto &amp; Doktor Alfred present their dance floor specials. Nicolas Ojesto, the partner of well known House producer Abel Ramos with Tribal &amp; Tech-House remix, Darkroom Remix is quite electronic made with kinda Disco esthetics in breakdown. Massa &amp; Doktor Alfred drive version with vocal percussions is pretty groovy&hellip; Enjoy&hellip;', '&nbsp;', NULL, 'Voltereto &amp; Doktor Alfred - Tinajo (Original Mix)<br />\r\nVoltereto &amp; Doktor Alfred - Tinajo (Nicolas Ojesto Remix)<br />\r\nVoltereto &amp; Doktor Alfred - Tinajo (Darkroom Remix)<br />\r\nVoltereto &amp; Doktor Alfred - Tinajo (Massa &amp; Doktor Alfred Remix)', 1, '2016-07-19 12:07:24', '2016-07-19 12:07:24'),
(1339, 145, 'Zukunftstraume, JB General - Perfect Technique', 'CTS145113', '2011-06-16', '1339_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/perfect-technique/378334', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/perfect-technique/378334', 'Another Techno EP by Zukunfstraume at CTS Records. For this time coming out with Perfect Technique EP produced in partnership with JB General, and becoming an international Techno project. Progressive Techno remixed by Luis Noic from Spain, Luigi Grecola from Italy, and version from Hungary by David Temessi&hellip; VIVA TECHNO!', '&nbsp;', NULL, 'Zukunftstraume, JB General - Perfect Technique (Original Mix)<br />\r\nZukunftstraume, JB General - Perfect Technique (Luis Noic Remix)<br />\r\nZukunftstraume, JB General - Perfect Technique (Luigi Grecola Remix)<br />\r\nZukunftstraume, JB General - Perfect Technique (David Temessi Remix)', 1, '2016-07-19 12:03:26', '2016-07-19 12:03:26'),
(1351, 146, 'CTSensors EP vol.5', 'CTS146113', '2011-06-23', '1351_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/ctsensors-ep-volume-5/381821', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/ctsensors-ep-volume-5/381821', 'Last CTSensors EP in Spring is marked with genres from Techno to House. As more to House side sounds becomes more deep, like announce of upcoming Summer&hellip; Deep and Minimal Tech &ldquo;Essou&rdquo; by Kevin Budraitis from Russia, Ukrainian sound-producer Dima Leon4ik has his debut at CTS Records with hot &amp; deep tech-house tune &ldquo;Give You Pleasure&rdquo;. Best Track in Ukraine contest winner in Tech-House genre Komplektov with new slick Deep House tune &ldquo;One Flew Over&rdquo;. X-Tropic together with Russel S also in the EP with their Progressive work &ldquo;Tomorrow Day&rdquo;&hellip; Stay tuned&hellip;', '&nbsp;', NULL, 'Komplektov - One Flew Over<br />\r\nDima Leon4ik - Give You Pleasure<br />\r\nKevin Budraitis - Essou (Original Mix)<br />\r\nX-Tropic &amp; Russel S - Tomorrow Day (Original Mix)', 1, '2016-07-19 12:00:00', '2016-07-19 12:00:00'),
(1353, 147, 'CTSensors EP vol.6', 'CTS147113', '2011-07-07', '1353_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/ctsensors-ep-vol-6/390097', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/ctsensors-ep-vol-6/390097', 'Start your summer with melodic Techno and Progressive harmonies. Next CTS brand EP shows melodic and pumping moods in a one. As usual unreleased before fresh productions are included. &ldquo;Long Way&rdquo; Techno beats traditionally from Klaster, Roman Sweet shifted the emphasis in &ldquo;Dreams&rdquo;, like pitch bend wheel moves on percussion synthesizer, as a result non standard view to melodic minimal sound. Metropolis strong Techno tune by Second Stage duo and Minimal &amp; Prog influenced Techno production &ldquo;My Baby is You&rdquo; by To Hard-Zen&hellip; pump up the dance floor!', '&nbsp;', NULL, 'Klaster - Long Way<br />\r\nTo Hard-Zen - My Baby is You<br />\r\nRoman Sweet - Dreams<br />\r\nSecond Stage - Metropolis', 1, '2016-07-19 11:57:24', '2016-07-19 11:57:24'),
(1354, 148, 'CTSensors EP vol.7', 'CTS148113', '2011-07-21', '1354_s.jpg', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/ctsensors-ep-volume-7/397478', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/ctsensors-ep-volume-7/397478', 'The seventh edition continues the mood of energy CTSensors previous EP. Dark tech-house trip &quot;Vote&quot; (Deep Tech Version) by Russian Techno producer Bullshit Bingo, explosive Tech-House tune &quot;Sticky&quot; by Materia &amp; Roman Sweet also two Minimal tracks: Funky &amp; soft &quot;Just Do It&quot; by Dee Mares and &quot;Zone of Turbulence&quot; by AparateX built on deformated &amp; filtered atmospheres&hellip;', '&nbsp;', NULL, 'AparateX - Zone Of Turbulance<br />\r\nDee Mares - Just Do It<br />\r\nMateria &amp; Roman Sweet - Sticky<br />\r\nBullshit Bingo - Vote (Deep Tech Version)', 1, '2016-07-19 11:55:38', '2016-07-19 11:55:38');
