(1359, 149, 'struCTS vol.3', 'CTS149113', '2011-07-14', '1359_s.jpg', 'https://www.beatport.com/#release/structs-3/393327', 'https://www.beatport.com/#release/structs-3/393327', 'As usual most wanted tracks only are on board. Next struCTS compilation is mostly about different colors of pick time sounds. Tech-House tunes &quot;Picasso&quot; by Fallhead from Germany, &quot;Toys Trombone&quot; by British duo Dauphin, &quot;Spin the Records&quot; vocal Tech-House track by Stanislav Kaligula and Italian beats, tight Maxitronica remix of &quot;Disco Ball&quot; by Alexander Fog. &quot;Funky Rif&quot; - hot, original track by &quot;The Best Track in Ukraine&quot; contest winner in House genre El Mariachi. Another side of the EP is dedicated to Techno vibes Aquabeat project is present with three collaborations: &quot;Rum &amp; Sambooca&quot; made with Vein Litterback, and &quot;Earth 2160&quot; by Aquabeat &amp; Yan Oxygen, and Minimal influenced remix for Ukrainian duo work &quot;Whisky&quot; by Louie Cut from Portugal. One else tune from Aquabeat - &quot;Inception&quot; in original version, also Yan Oxygen&rsquo;s remix of Sergio Mega&rsquo;s &quot;To Catch the Last Train&quot; and dark tune &quot;Long Way&quot; by Klaster&hellip; Enjoy&hellip;', '', NULL, 'Sergio Mega - To Catch The Last Train (Yan Oxygen Remix)<br />\r\nAquabeat - Whisky (Louie Cut Remix)<br />\r\nDauphin - Toys Trombone<br />\r\nAquabeat - Inception (Original Mix)<br />\r\nKlaster - Way to West (Original Mix)<br />\r\nAquabeat &amp; Yan Oxygen - Earth 2160 (Original Mix)<br />\r\nEl Mariachi - Funky Riff<br />\r\nAquabeat &amp; Vein Litterback - Rum &amp; Sambuca (Original Mix)<br />\r\nStanislav Kaligula - Spin the Records (Happy Funky Original Mix)<br />\r\nAlexander Fog - Disco Ball (Maxitronica Remix)<br />\r\nFallhead - Picasso', 1, '2016-09-20 12:59:25', '2016-09-20 12:59:25'),
(1364, 150, 'CTSensors EP vol.8 (Chill-Out Edition)', 'CTS151113', '2011-08-03', '1364_s.jpg', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/ctsensors-volume-8-chill-out-edition/402949', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/ctsensors-volume-8-chill-out-edition/402949', 'Traditionally, Summer CTS Records adds soft chill-out melodies to brand selection, and as usual all the EP tracks are get to the Top of Releasepromo Downtempo chart. Trip-Hop &quot;Secret&quot; by Ikiro, sea beach dream &quot;Stormy Coast&quot; by Ixidor, emotional &quot;Gaya&quot; by Ukrainian composer Victor Sviridov and debut track at CTS Records &quot;My Girl&quot; by Stereo Andrew&hellip; pure relaxation&hellip;', '&nbsp;', NULL, 'Ikiro - Secret<br />\r\nIxidor - Stormy Coast<br />\r\nVictor Sviridov - Gaya<br />\r\nStereo Andrew - My Girl', 1, '2016-07-19 11:50:12', '2016-07-19 11:50:12'),
(1365, 151, 'Paul Funkee - Evening', 'CTS152113', '2011-08-11', '1365_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/evening/404608', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'We welcome Russian Techno talent Paul Funkee at CTS Records. Deep, dark melodic &quot;Evening&quot; made with Progressive influences have original harmony and hypnotic breakdown. Remixed by Ukrainian Techno masters Slackers Project together with Pirania; and  Artur Grek &amp; Tim F.Resh show their Tech-House and Prog view in the remix&hellip; play it loud!...', '&nbsp;', NULL, 'Paul Funkee - Evening (Original Mix)<br />\r\nPaul Funkee - Evening (Artur Grek &amp; Tim F.Resh Remix)<br />\r\nPaul Funkee - Evening (Slackers Project &amp; Piranya Remix)', 1, '2016-07-19 11:47:18', '2016-07-19 11:47:18'),
(1371, 152, 'CTSummer 2011', 'CTS150113', '2011-08-18', '1371_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/ctsummer-2011/436960', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'We are proud to announce #150 release at CTS records!<br />\r\nCTSummer 2011 compiled mixed by CTS founder Sergio Mega. Chilled selection of deep house, house and progressive tracks refresh like sea breeze, what could be better in hot summer time... Release will be in stores in August, also available as unmixed compilation... Enjoy', '&nbsp;', NULL, 'Fresh &amp; Majectic - Jazzy<br />\r\nKomplektov - Corners of Mind<br />\r\nArtem Zest - Ovine<br />\r\nDee Mares - Gala<br />\r\nSergio Mega feat. Seva Solncev - At Night (Tina Valen Dub)<br />\r\nOleg Soul - Rain<br />\r\nKomplektov - Coming<br />\r\nRoma Fresh pres. N.A.K. - At Night<br />\r\nAlex Love - Deep (Alex Love Remix)<br />\r\nIkiro - Without You (Vocal Mix)', 1, '2016-07-19 11:44:12', '2016-07-19 11:44:12'),
