(1438, 183, 'CTS Miami 2012', 'CTS183123', '2012-03-23', '1438_s.jpg', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/cts-miami-2012/885379', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/cts-miami-2012/885379', 'CTS Miami sampler is out as always in March,&nbsp;during well known Winter Music Conference.&nbsp;Compilation is dedicated mostly to House music,&nbsp;which is so In Miami style.&nbsp;This year CTS go through the house genre,&nbsp;with tech-house and deep to techno sound which is traditional to label.', '', NULL, 'Sergio Mega - Upper (Slackers Project Remix)<br />\r\nDima Leon4ik - Inhalation<br />\r\nNinoHengst - Egoshooter<br />\r\nEl Mariachi - Amigos<br />\r\nMissy Jay - Isla<br />\r\nP.O.ison - Summertime', 1, '2016-09-26 11:41:51', '2016-09-26 11:41:51'),
(1440, 184, 'CTSonics EP vol.2', 'CTS184123', '2013-03-27', '1440_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/ctsonics-ep-vol-2/886050', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', '&nbsp;', NULL, NULL, 'Bob Fanzidon - Doppler<br />\r\nRoman Sweet - Export<br />\r\nMechanical Wave - Proof<br />\r\nEL Sam &amp; Dave Droid - Toys (Original Mix)', 1, '2016-06-07 15:50:31', '2016-06-07 15:50:31'),
(1443, 185, 'Favorites vol.2', 'CTS185123', '2012-03-30', '1443_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/favorites-vol-2/886060', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'From 100 Best Track in Ukraine contest finalists we selected most wanted tracks, which amounted this multigenre compilation. It consists of almost full spectrum of the dance music from chill-Out to Techno. Post Bass tune by Queensway only confirms his victory of the Best Track and the main prise Grand Prix, as well as Ikiro&lsquo;s Red Line, track winner in Chill-Out nomination.  Also in this compilation you can get three tech-house tracks by Aleksandr Kit, Artur Grek &amp; Tim F.Resh and Konstantin Yoodza, techno vibes by Emerix, broken beats by Amarilyo &amp; Bratus and more Chill-Ourt staff from BrainNebula, DaGro, RockMeister and SirDuke... enjoy', NULL, NULL, 'Queensway - Teletype-Several<br />\r\nIkiro - Red Line (Original Mix)<br />\r\nBrainNebula - One Man Vision<br />\r\nAmarilyo &amp; Bratus - Woopoo Rast<br />\r\nSirDuke - All My Loving<br />\r\nAlexander Kit - Nothin On The Radio (Original Mix)<br />\r\nRockMeister - For You<br />\r\nKonstantin Yoodza - Birdlike<br />\r\nEmerix - Unsuitability<br />\r\nDaGro - Story Of My Life<br />\r\nArtur Grek &amp; Tim F.Resh - Discoteka', 1, '2016-06-07 15:47:11', '2016-06-07 15:47:11'),
(1445, 186, 'CTSonics EP vol.3', 'CTS186123', '2012-04-06', '1445_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/ctsonics-ep-vol-3/888028', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'Next mounthly CTS brand EP is out with four fresh tracks. Groovy &amp; deep Tech-House tune  made by Russian dj &amp; producer Bullshit Bingo; techno sound is presented by To Hard-Zen; juicy Progressive production by DJ Ubee and San.Dy is back with new deep &amp; melodic track... enjoy', NULL, NULL, 'San.Dy - Sky<br />\r\nDJ Ubee - Walking Through<br />\r\nTo Hard-Zen - Good Day<br />\r\nBullshit Bingo - D Night', 1, '2016-06-07 15:44:29', '2016-06-07 15:44:29'),
(1446, 187, 'struCTS vol.5', 'CTS187123', '2012-04-13', '1446_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/structs-5/889384', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'Fifth edition of struCTS compilation traditionaly includes most wanted seasonal tracks. Yan Oxygen is here with three techno proggy tracks from his latest artist album named &quot;The Album&quot;, Dub Makers tech-house remix with syncopic bass to Sergio Mega&lsquo;s tune &quot;Upper&quot;, dubstep by PoLMaX, two techno productions by Aleksandr Life an by Techno Animals and also weighty chill-out selection including tracks by Queensway, DJ KoT and Victor Sviridov... enjoy', '', NULL, 'Yan Oxygen - Change<br />\r\nAleksandr Life - Idea<br />\r\nSergio Mega - Upper (Dub Makers Remix)<br />\r\nYan Oxygen - Versailles<br />\r\nDJ KoT - Caveman&lsquo;s Valentine<br />\r\nQueensway - Darling<br />\r\nYan Oxygen - Monoloc<br />\r\nVictor Sviridov - Contemplator<br />\r\nTechno Animals - Allure Demon<br />\r\nPoLMaX - Delusion', 1, '2016-09-20 12:59:10', '2016-09-20 12:59:10'),
(1450, 188, 'Sergio Mega - Gogol', 'CTS188123', '2012-04-20', '1450_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/sergio-mega-gogol/896035', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'Next Sergio Mega&lsquo;s single release is out in April. Groovy tech-house tune with vocal percussion and in addition with an original screem sound which have an extraordiary story. Camera team of One Plus One TV channel has made a night shooting in Carpathian mountains. The sound catched by the microphone impressed and inspired them to make a special program about another worlds and unexplained phenomenas named &quot;Otherworldly Ukraine&quot;.  Then Sergio was invited as a studio expert to discuss this sound origin. And now Gogol release is presented to your attention! Seven remixes plus original mix are included to the release. Different sides of techno are in EP palette, proggy &amp; tech-house  remix by Dima Leon4ik,  expressive techo remix with rising intro by The Best Track in Ukraine contest Techno nomination winners - Mechanical Wave duo, techno with minimal adds by Klaster, textural rhythmes by Roman Sweet, techy percussive vibes by Bockscar and deep tech-house &amp; funky remix from german sound-explorer NinoHengst which coming with extended twelve minutes version..  The sound of Carpathian screaming creature is using in this release, with the courtesy agree of the journalist and TV presenter &quot;One Plus One&quot; TV channel Julia Dyachuk...Stay tuned...', NULL, NULL, 'Sergio Mega - Gogol (Original Mix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega - Gogol (Klaster Remix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega - Gogol (Bockscar Remix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega - Gogol (NinoHengst Extended Mix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega - Gogol (NinoHengst Remix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega - Gogol (Roman Sweet Remix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega - Gogol (Dima Leon4ik Remix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega - Gogol (Mechanical Wave Remix)', 1, '2016-06-07 15:39:52', '2016-06-07 15:39:52'),
(1453, 189, 'CTSonics EP vol.4', 'CTS189123', '2012-04-27', '1453_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/ctsonics-ep-vol-4/901465', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'Fourth CTSonics, CTS Records brand EP is coming out at the end of April with spring buds and green grass. In this volume we are happy to introduce German talented duo - DIGITALmusikanten with hot tech-house tune Men of Udakai. By the way, this duo project is managed by well known Dutch DJ &amp; producer Woody van Eyden. Also in CTSonics part four crew, a rising star of underground scene, Italian female dj - Missy Jay with her next tech-house deep &amp; funky track at CTS &quot;Lost Headphones&quot;. Then we go deeper and deeper with a really deep production called &quot;Name&quot; by Esford from Kyiv and after that come back to Italian side with techno groovy &quot;Viaje Largo feat.  Karina &quot; by Marco Piangiamore from sunny Sardigna...', NULL, NULL, 'Esford - Name<br />\r\nMissy Jay - Lost Headphones<br />\r\nDIGITALmusikanten - Men of Udakai<br />\r\nMarco Piangiamore - Viaje Largo feat. Karina', 1, '2016-06-07 15:37:40', '2016-06-07 15:37:40'),
(1456, 190, 'Esford - We Trust EP', 'CTS190123', '2012-05-04', '1456_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/esford-we-trust-ep/905950', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'It&lsquo;s a pleasure to welcome new Ukrainian talent Esford at CTS Records! Originally from Liepaya, Latvia, now lives and works in the capital of Ukraine, Kiev. Two banging tracks EP is coming out at fourth of May, the best time for the first Open Air parties. Groovy sound so typical for author underlines both tracks of the EP. Techno production &quot;Black Room&quot; with aggressive dynamic leads and dark vocals, and Tech-House tune &quot;We Trust&quot; with deep influences in rhytmic factures and pulsative built up vibes in juicy breakdown... explosive<br />', NULL, NULL, 'Esford - We Trust (Original Mix)<br />\r\nEsford - Black Room (Original Mix)', 1, '2016-06-07 15:35:36', '2016-06-07 15:35:36'),
(1458, 191, 'Favorites vol.3', 'CTS191123', '2012-05-11', '1458_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/favorites-vol-3/906684', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'With Favorites volume 3 compilation CTS Records continue to release most wanted tracks from The Best Track in Ukraine contest finalists. Multigenre again but mostly focused on Techno side of the electronic music. Chill-Out by DJ KoT opens the collection, Deep House tune by Ikiro continue, after follows Electro Proggy productions by Amarilyo, FrozeN, The Crime and Igor Graphite, then coming Techno selection including works by El Mariachi, Big&amp;Little, Jin Haze and Claud... fat and hot!', NULL, NULL, 'DJ KoT - Caveman&lsquo;s Valentine<br />\r\nFrozeN - Tetris<br />\r\nEl Mariachi - Make Your Choice<br />\r\nClaud - Gray Clouds<br />\r\nJin Haze - Moonlight Persistence<br />\r\nIkiro - Mr.Zee (Soul Full House Mix)<br />\r\nAmarilyo - Adrenalin<br />\r\nIgor Graphite - Fly<br />\r\nBig&amp;little - Circle<br />\r\nThe Crime - Desperate', 1, '2016-06-07 15:32:56', '2016-06-07 15:32:56'),
(1462, 192, 'CTSonics EP vol.5', 'CTS192123', '2012-05-18', '1462_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/ctsonics-ep-vol-5/913328', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'CTS Records presents house flavored selection with fifth CTSonics EP which is coming out in May. Most wanted genre at any Beach party or open Air is presented in this EP. House music is very wide and combines many shades and sub directions, some of them appear in CTSonics volume 5. Influenced by filtered side of house new production by Esford is deep and funky, as well as tech-house tune by German DJ &amp; producer NinoHengst and deep house track Dee Mares. Russian sound producer Danny Mirando submits house work with an analogue synth sounds impurities.. rock da party!...<br />', NULL, NULL, 'Esford - Mod<br />\r\nDee Mares - High Clouds<br />\r\nNinoHengst - Rocking Mouth<br />\r\nDanny Mirando - Desna River', 1, '2016-06-07 15:30:09', '2016-06-07 15:30:09'),
(1465, 193, 'Zukunftstraume - Voyage', 'CTS193123', '2012-05-31', '1465_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/zukunftstraume-voyage/918485', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'Single Voyage by Zukunftstraume, latest release of May ends CTS spring season. Original is supplemented with remix by JB General. Bouth tracks are made in traditional Techno esthetics, sound with deep influents, dark and trippy, plunges into the atmosphere of rhythmic pulsating gloom... feel vibrations...', NULL, NULL, 'Zukunftstraume - Voyage (Original Mix)<br />\r\nZukunftstraume - Voyage (JB General Remix)', 1, '2016-06-07 15:27:56', '2016-06-07 15:27:56'),
(1466, 194, 'Marfel - El Verano EP', 'CTS194123', '2012-06-08', '1466_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/marfel-el-verano-ep/923198', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'Three new strong, tight tracks by Italian DJ &amp; producer Marfel.&nbsp;Playing vinyl in Italy and German street festivals, German and British radioostations as well as at well known American Proton Radio, Marfel displayed this experience in his sound production. Mediterranean atmosphere of the EP supplemented with Detroit influents. Iberican moods are coming through the underground techno vibes, all three groovy, textural tunes are filled with varied percussions and deep piercing voices... outdoor sounds!', NULL, NULL, 'Marfel - En La Playa<br />\r\nMarfel - Noche Ibizenca<br />\r\nMarfel - Una Noche De Verano Al  Ritmo De Los Congas', 1, '2016-06-07 15:25:28', '2016-06-07 15:25:28'),
(1468, 195, 'CTSonics EP vol.6', 'CTS195123', '2012-06-15', '1468_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/ctsonics-ep-vol-6/925659', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'With sixth CTSonics EP CTS is coming back to techno side. Dark vibes and tight rhythms are immerse listeners in an atmosphere of underground sound. Blow up your summer!', NULL, NULL, 'San Ko - Resistance<br />\r\nBockscar - Ink<br />\r\nChameleon - Dark Side Summer<br />\r\nRoman Sweet - 49th Avenue', 1, '2016-06-07 15:22:49', '2016-06-07 15:22:49'),
(1470, 196, 'struCTS vol.6', 'CTS196123', '2012-06-22', '1470_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/structs-6/925641', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'Next struCTS compilation propose pretty energetic rhythms: two deep house productions by Esford and Dee Mares also two tech-house tracks by DIGITALmusikanten and Konstantin Yoodza, then five different shades of techno sound by Emerix, El Mariachi, Aleksandr Life, Marco Piangiamore and Klaster&lsquo;s remix to Sergio Mega&lsquo;s Gogol tune. And finally progressive work by Bob Fanzidon close selection... shake your body!!!', '', NULL, 'Konstantin Yoodza - Birdlike<br />\r\nDIGITALmusikanten - Men of Udakai<br />\r\nEsford - Name<br />\r\nDee Mares - High Clouds<br />\r\nMarco Piangiamore - Viaje Largo feat. Karina<br />\r\nAleksandr Life - Next<br />\r\nEmerix - Unsuitability<br />\r\nEl Mariachi - Make Your Choice<br />\r\nBob Fanzidon - Doppler<br />\r\nSergio Mega - Gogol (Klaster Remix)', 1, '2016-09-20 12:59:02', '2016-09-20 12:59:02'),
(1472, 197, 'CTSonics EP vol.7 (Broken Beats)', 'CTS197123', '2012-07-12', '1472_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/ctsonics-ep-vol-7-broken-beats/937823', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'Next CTS Records brand EP is non usual for regular label direction, but it is continue summer tradition to release different forms of sound. This time we go to broken beat side with its shadows: breaks, drum&lsquo;n&lsquo;base and dubstep... enjoy...', NULL, NULL, 'Broukez - Fortress<br />\r\nShurmenkoff - Strider<br />\r\nDmitriy Yusupov - Night', 1, '2016-06-07 15:17:14', '2016-06-07 15:17:14'),
(1475, 198, 'struCTS vol.7 (chill & deep)', 'CTS198123', '2012-07-19', '1475_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/structs-7-chill-and-deep/942005', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'Summer time require mild and relaxing sounds. Next struCTS chill &amp; deep compilation is dedicated to chill-out and deep-house. Ten chill-out tracks by The Best Track in Ukraine 2011 winner Queensway, The Best Track in Ukraine 2010 winner DaGro, well known ukrainian composer Tka4, also tracks by Ikiro, BrainNebula, DJ KoT, SirDuke, RockMeister, Amarilyo &amp; Bratus; then three deep-house tunes by Dee Mares, Esford and one more production by Ikiro. relax..... enjoy...', '', NULL, 'Ikiro - Secret<br />\r\nDee Mares - Gala<br />\r\nIkiro - Red Line<br />\r\nBrainNebula - One Man Vision<br />\r\nQueensway - Teletype-Several<br />\r\nEsford - Name<br />\r\nDJ KoT - Caveman&lsquo;s Valentine<br />\r\nRockMeister - For You<br />\r\nSirDuke - All My Loving<br />\r\nAmarilyo &amp; Bratus - Woopoo Rast<br />\r\nIkiro - Feel So Deep<br />\r\nTka4 - More<br />\r\nDaGro - Story Of My Life', 1, '2016-09-20 12:58:41', '2016-09-20 12:58:41'),
(1477, 199, 'Brutal Kids - Kinetic', 'CTS199123', '2012-10-08', '1477_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/brutal-kids-kinetic/951626', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'CTS Records presents new release by Brutal Kids - DJ duo based in sunny south of Ukraine. Finalists of The Best Track in Ukraine contest, host own radioshow at Kiss FM, submit progressive beats between mainstream and underground in their two mixes of Kinetic tune. Remix by DJ Ubee also made in progressive esthetics make the complete palette... select your colour', NULL, NULL, 'Brutal Kids - Kinetic (Original Mix)<br />\r\nBrutal Kids - Kinetic (DJ Ubee Remix)<br />\r\nBrutal Kids - Kinetic (Brutal Kids Remix)', 1, '2016-06-07 14:56:35', '2016-06-07 14:56:35'),
(1479, 200, 'CTS 200', 'CTS200123', '2012-08-24', '1479_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/cts-200/957619', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'We are proud to announce CTS #200 release. <br />\r\nSince 2004 CTS records has kept direction between House and Techno sound, this trend is reflected in the compilation. Selection of &laquo;must have&raquo; tunes which will always fit to any party, is presented in it. Tracks and remixes by DJ Pierre, Sergio Mega, Yan Oxygen, Louie Cut, Aquabeat, Kotov &amp; Andre Wilde, Truati, Gaga, DJ Lion, Nathan Barato, M.I.D.I., Juan DDD, Slackers Project and more, dancefloor burners, will satisfy djs and clubbers taste &amp; requirments... 201 release is not far off, keep dancing...<br />', NULL, NULL, 'Yan Oxygen - Endless Way (Original Mix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega feat. Niels Von Geyer - She Loves The Rain (Yan Oxygen Remix)<br />\r\nM.I.D.I. - Back Time (Slackers Project Remix)<br />\r\nAquabeat - Inception (Gaga Remix)<br />\r\nAquabeat feat. Rey-Na - Cocaine (Truati Remix)<br />\r\nAquabeat - Whisky (Louie Cut Remix)<br />\r\nYan Oxygen - System Off (Bockscar Remix)<br />\r\nDeb feat. MC Yug - Plastic Toys (Nick Zero Prog Mix)<br />\r\nYan Oxygen - Revolution<br />\r\nYan Oxygen - System Off<br />\r\nAquabeat feat. Rey-Na - Ride The Time (Sergio Mega Remix)<br />\r\nAquabeat feat. Rey-Na - Cocaine (Vein Litterback Remix)<br />\r\nAquabeat and Yan Oxygen - Earth 2160 (Juan DDD Fucking Remix)<br />\r\nYan Oxygen - Unknown Science<br />\r\nFresh and Majestic - Funky House<br />\r\nMantrique - Optimistika<br />\r\nShiz - Insomnia (Sergio Mega Remix)<br />\r\nKotov &amp; Andre Wilde - Jump (Nathan Barato Anti Vox Remix)<br />\r\nYan Oxygen - Stay (Original Mix)<br />\r\nSlackers Project - Disco Rocker<br />\r\nKotov &amp; Andre Wilde - Mini Human Beings (Original Mix)<br />\r\nAquabeat and Yan Oxygen - Earth 2160 (Original Mix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega - Stereoland (Club Mix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega feat. Niels von Geyer - Dance No