(1492, 206, 'CTSonics EP vol.10', 'CTS206123', '2012-11-14', '1492_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/ctsonics-ep-vol-10/995153', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'Next CTSonics tenth EP is comming out in November. From Deep and slow dance T-Fain&acute;s Memories, through Tech-House Bullshit Bingo&acute;s Miss Gift, then go to Techno side with Tokyo Police by Chameleon and Restless Night - guitar motive tune by James Laben... keep on rhythm', NULL, NULL, 'T-Fain - Memories<br />\r\nChameleon - Tokyo Police<br />\r\nJames Laben - Restless Night<br />\r\nBullshit Bingo - Miss Gift', 1, '2016-06-07 12:48:59', '2016-06-07 12:48:59'),
(1494, 207, 'Marfel - Ibiza EP', 'CTS207123', '2012-12-11', '1494_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/marfel-ibiza-ep/1009816', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'Another EP by Italian Dj &amp; producer Marfel at CTS Records.<br />\r\nPlaying vinyl in Italy and German street festivals, German and British radiostations as well as at well known American Proton Radio, Marfel illustrates this experience in his sound production. Usual for Marfel Mediterranean atmosphere is supplemented with Detroit influents. Three new groovy, pumping tech-house tracks with tribal and Iberican moods are made for underground dancefloor, EP filled with varied percussions and deep piercing voices... boooom!', NULL, NULL, 'Marfel - Ibiza Funk<br />\r\nMarfel - Evissa Night<br />\r\nMarfel - El Sol Es Muy Caliente', 1, '2016-06-07 12:45:24', '2016-06-07 12:45:24'),
