(1515, 218, 'Yan Oxygen - Kharkov', 'CTS218133', '2013-01-13', '1515_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/yan-oxygen-kharkov/1016826', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'New single release Kharkov by Ukrainian techno specialist, dj &amp; producer Yan Oxygen is coming out with four remixes. Melancholic motive of the original track have an energy inside, powerful leads and tight beats reflects strict moods of Kharkov city. Andy Mart shows deep, melodic prog &amp; techno vibes, Sunheat&acute;s groove goes to more active side, deep tech-house proggy BiohazArt remix is flavored with twisted bassline, Klaster completes collection with underground techno &amp; percussive rhythms... dance&acute;n&acute;think!', NULL, NULL, 'Yan Oxygen - Kharkov (Original Mix)<br />\r\nYan Oxygen - Kharkov (Klaster Remix)<br />\r\nYan Oxygen - Kharkov (Sunheat Remix)<br />\r\nYan Oxygen - Kharkov (BiohazArt Remix)<br />\r\nYan Oxygen - Kharkov (Andy Mart Remix)', 1, '2016-06-07 12:19:21', '2016-06-07 12:19:21'),
