(1524, 220, 'CTStreams EP vol.1', 'CTS220133', '2013-02-07', '1524_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/ctstreams-ep-vol-1/1034714', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'CTS Records presents new EP series CTStreams. With first edition in 2013 CTS goes to roots of sound, to authentic melodies, vocals and instruments. All tracks are made in Tech-House esthetics, Mamay submits India influenced instrumental European view. Groovy, track with native American woodwinds by Mexican sound producer Sueal and Indian vocal full of percussion track with broken beats by Veleev... let the beat goes on!...', NULL, NULL, 'Sueal - Incredible Love (Original Mix)<br />\r\nVeleev - 48 24<br />\r\nMamay - Aswem Harps (Original Mix)', 1, '2016-06-06 15:50:37', '2016-06-06 15:50:37'),
(1527, 221, 'Heal - Virginity EP', 'CTS221133', '2013-02-22', '1527_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/heal-virginity-ep/1044235', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'If you looking for bright deep tracks, Virginity EP is for you. Californian duo Heal submits multilayered &amp; atmospheric sound. Palette of House and Tech-House flavored with vocalises, unostentatious percussions, and parts of speech by world famous Charlie Chaplin, from The Great Dictator film entwined into headline Virginity track. All three tunes are made in Deep esthetics with Ambient influences.. dancing on clouds...', NULL, NULL, 'Heal - Tigers<br />\r\nHeal - Azizam<br />\r\nHeal - Virginity', 1, '2016-06-06 15:48:07', '2016-06-06 15:48:07'),
(1528, 222, 'CTStreams EP vol.2', 'CTS222133', '1970-01-01', '1528_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/ctstreams-ep-vol-2/1046765', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'February transatlantic edition of CTStreams is groovy and techy. CTS Records welcomes two European and one American sound producers. German deep &amp; tech house artist NinoHengst with new track 9 Inch, Pablo caballero from Argetina with heady techno tune Red Rum and Dutch Tim Deetakt with his new pumping and deep tech-house production Transatlantic Tunnel. At the end of 2012 Well known Traxsource choosed the track of Tim Deetakt as #1 Esential techno track.. dance your best...', NULL, NULL, 'Tim Deetakt - Transatlantic Tunnel<br />\r\nNinoHengst - 9 Inch<br />\r\nPablo Caballero - Red Rum', 1, '2016-06-06 15:45:20', '2016-06-06 15:45:20'),
(1530, 223, 'Esford - About You', 'CTS223133', '2013-03-08', '1530_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/esford-about-you/1052304', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'Spring begins and Esford comes out with his first single release at CTS named About You. Artist as always is faithful to his deep direction therefore original is implemented in groovy and techy house way. Release is adorned with 2 remixes, both are deep as well. Deep house with some funk influents by The Best Track in Ukraine House nomination winner - Deepstereo and distinctive 2 step and athmospheric deep view by Maxim Play... dive, swim up and dance...', NULL, NULL, 'Esford - About You (Original Mix)<br />\r\nEsford - About You (Maxim Play Remix)<br />\r\nEsford - About You (Deepstereo Remix)', 1, '2016-06-06 15:39:48', '2016-06-06 15:39:48'),
(1532, 224, 'Favorites vol.4 Miami Edition', 'CTS224133', '2013-03-15', '1532_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/favorites-vol-4-miami-edition/1055187', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'Fourth edition of Favorites compilation is dedicated to Winter Music Conference in Miami. Fifteen tracks selected from the Best Track in Ukraine contest tracks finalists. All tunes went through the tight competition... Make your choice!...', NULL, NULL, 'Riolie - Moor (Original Mix)<br />\r\nNarayana - Let Your Body Move<br />\r\nAtom - Avogadro<br />\r\nIkiro - Midnight Traffic (Original Mix)<br />\r\nQueensway - Path To Sea (Atmospheric Re-edit)<br />\r\nRaketa4000 - Which One Is For The Soul<br />\r\nAlex Love - Summer End (Original Mix)<br />\r\nDmitry Deep - In Da Base (Original Mix)<br />\r\nAmarilyo - Happy Time<br />\r\nNeopoly Project - Deep Day<br />\r\nGeorgos Dansio - Piece Of Paradise<br />\r\nAlex Love - Old Ways (Original Mix)<br />\r\nAmarilyo &amp; Peter Und Der Wolf - Porno Twist<br />\r\nYuri Petrovski - Autumn (Original Mix)<br />\r\nPoLMaX &amp; Igor Graphite - Qwerty (Original Mix)', 1, '2016-06-06 15:35:35', '2016-06-06 15:35:35'),
(1535, 225, 'CTStreams EP vol.3', 'CTS225133', '2013-03-28', '1535_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/ctstreams-ep-vol-3/1062389', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'Third CTSreams is deep atmospheric and funky - all in one. Maxim Play submits groovy impressions of his Amsterdam adventures in &quot;Lost in Jordan&quot; track, deep &amp; light vibes in &quot;Base&quot; by Heal, and tech-house deep tune &quot;Something&quot; by Dima Leon4ik with syncopic percussions and jazzy vocals.. pump up the deep...', NULL, NULL, 'Maxim Play - Lost In Jordan<br />\r\nHeal - Base<br />\r\nDima Leon4ik - Something', 1, '2016-06-06 15:32:39', '2016-06-06 15:32:39'),
(1537, 226, 'struCTS vol.9', 'CTS226133', '2013-04-12', '1537_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/structs-9/1068999', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'Nine part of struCTS compilation series is about House and Techno. Spring choice of tracks by Yan Oxygen, Heal, Bockscar, Slackers Project &amp; Pirania, Esford, Marfel, Dee Mares, Cheise, Brutal Kids with remixes by Klaster, Deepstereo and Dima Leon4ik... dance, dance, dance, ignite your spring...', '', NULL, 'Yan Oxygen - Kharkov (Klaster Remix)<br />\r\nYan Oxygen - Kharkov (Original Mix)<br />\r\nBockscar - Ink<br />\r\nHeal - Virginity<br />\r\nMarfel - Evissa Night<br />\r\nEsford - About You (Deepstereo Remix)<br />\r\nSlackers Project &amp; Pirania - Hands Up (Dima Leon4ik Remix)<br />\r\nDee Mares - High Clouds<br />\r\nCheise - WGI<br />\r\nBrutal Kids - Kinetic (Brutal Kids Remix)', 1, '2016-09-20 12:58:23', '2016-09-20 12:58:23'),
(1538, 227, 'Yan Oxygen - All The Heroes Are Dead', 'CTS227133', '2013-04-19', '1538_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/yan-oxygen-all-the-heroes-are-dead/1074360', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'Another big tune by Yan Oxygen is coming out at CTS. Track is dark and light in same time, based on mystic melody, which follows from one remix to another. Juicy and Techy Original mix differs by syncopic base and synth elements. Californian duo Heal deliver their minimal and deep rework, Argentinian Pablo Caballero submits stright techno beats stained of sweeps and FXs with floating pitch, progressive remix by  Kain with shades of electro vibes and additional voxes emphasizes the idea of the original and finalize the release.. turn off your lamp and dance...', NULL, NULL, 'Yan Oxygen - All The Heroes Are Dead (Original Mix)<br />\r\nYan Oxygen - All The Heroes Are Dead (Heal Remix)<br />\r\nYan Oxygen - All The Heroes Are Dead (Pablo Caballero Remix)<br />\r\nYan Oxygen - All The Heroes Are Dead (Kain Remix)', 1, '2016-06-06 15:21:30', '2016-06-06 15:21:30'),
(1541, 228, 'James Laben - Bingo', 'CTS228133', '2013-05-03', '1541_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/james-laben-bingo/1082066', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'Good continue for techno theme at CTS, James Laben with Bingo single release. Three different shades of techno sound are presented, rolling over the break and growing up to the drop original mix, funky tech remix by Epic Therapy and tech-house groovy version by Gitech... Wear your favorite shoes and dance...<br />\r\n<br />', NULL, NULL, 'James Laben - Bingo (Original Mix)<br />\r\nJames Laben - Bingo (Epic Therapy Remix)<br />\r\nJames Laben - Bingo (Gitech Remix)', 1, '2016-05-20 16:16:21', '2016-05-20 16:16:21'),
(1542, 229, 'CTStreams EP vol.4', 'CTS229133', '2013-05-10', '1542_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/ctstreams-ep-vol-4/1085060', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'Next CTS brand EP impregnated with old school influences. House and techno sound palette is presented. House work Pushed with tech-house shades by Portuguese dj &amp; producer Marcio Morales, Roman Sweet submits soft techy vibes in his Reject It track, Shadow Dance - collaboration of Slark &amp; Feyser made between british &amp; detroit techno or better to say two in one styled production complete the package.. be cool! dance to the old school...', NULL, NULL, 'Marcio Morales - Pushed<br />\r\nRoman Sweet - Reject It<br />\r\nSlark &amp; Feyser - Shadow Dance', 1, '2016-05-20 16:12:39', '2016-05-20 16:12:39'),
(1545, 230, 'Jaroslaw - Eruption EP', 'CTS230133', '2013-05-23', '1545_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/eruption-ep/1093013', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'It&acute;s a pleasure to announce EP release of The Best Track in Ukraine contest winner in Progressive nomination - Jaroslaw. With two brand new tracks Jaroslaw shows the underground side of techno sound. Dark and deep both tunes are full of sounds. Interesting compositional work with bass lines and percussion worked out in detail... breathe deeply, dance longer...', NULL, NULL, 'Jaroslaw - Eruption<br />\r\nJaroslaw - Deep Inside', 1, '2016-05-20 16:10:40', '2016-05-20 16:10:40'),
(1547, 231, 'CTStreams EP vol.5', 'CTS231133', '2013-05-31', '1547_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/ctstreams-ep-vol-5/1097697', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'Fifth CTStreams EP is soft and melodic as an air in May. All three tracks are made in deep house esthetics, mild atmospheric track Kate by NEBULA(UA),Spring Snow with funky synth motive by Maxim Play and jazzy influenced Red Moon by Kirunchell with tight beats... relax and dance...', NULL, NULL, 'NEBULA(UA) - Kate<br />\r\nMaxim Play - Spring Snow<br />\r\nKirunchell - Red Moon', 1, '2016-05-20 16:06:46', '2016-05-20 16:06:46'),
(1549, 232, 'Terry Raze - Mars EP', 'CTS232133', '2013-06-07', '1549_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/terry-raze-mars-ep/1103160', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'Terry Raze submits fresh &amp; deep underground house sound in his two tracks EP. Mars with groovy base and hypnotic percussive tech-house vibes and &quot;Solid Ground&quot; tune is groovy as well made with vox &amp; synth elements, influeced with hot dub sounds...there is life on Mars, or there is no life on Mars... dance anyway...', NULL, NULL, 'Terry Raze - Mars<br />\r\nTerry Raze - Solid Ground', 1, '2016-05-20 16:04:48', '2016-05-20 16:04:48'),
(1551, 233, 'Sergio Mega - Vagator', 'CTS233133', '2013-06-14', '1551_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/sergio-mega-vagator/1107543', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'New sinngle release by Sergio Mega is permeated with authentic Hindu traditions and named after the legendary town in Goa famous by its atmosphere of freedom, beautiful wilde beach and hot top hill partys. Original extended mix is made with native Hindu vocals combined with groovy tech-house vibes. Amarilyo submits house remix with melodic breakdown, progressive remix by Kain with dirty juicy bassline is supplemented with Goa styled elements.. open your mind and dance...', NULL, NULL, 'Sergio Mega - Vagator (Extended Mix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega - Vagator (Amarilyo Remix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega - Vagator (Kain Remix)', 1, '2016-05-20 16:01:53', '2016-05-20 16:01:53'),
(1552, 234, 'Deepstereo - East or West EP', 'CTS234133', '2013-07-19', '1552_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/deepstereo-east-or-west-ep/1127230', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'Ukrainian house producer Deeepstereo, the winner of The Best Track in Ukraine house nomination is coming out with personal two tracks EP at CTS. Both tunes shows diferent shades of House music. Disco influenced progy and melodic West vs deep &amp; atmospheric asia stile vocalized &quot;East&quot;... East or West dance your best...', NULL, NULL, 'Deepstereo - East<br />\r\nDeepstereo - West', 1, '2016-05-20 15:58:43', '2016-05-20 15:58:43'),
(1555, 235, 'Heal - Sister', 'CTS235133', '2013-08-02', '1555_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/heal-sister/1133736', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'After personal deep EP release on CTS Heal is here again with Sister single. This time Californian duo  submits filtered House sound which is flavored with funky guitars and radio noises. Classic house bassline in the remix from Amarilyo, hot vibes with Caribbean percussions by Maxim Play and groovy deep summer beats by Deepstereo... everebody in da house!', NULL, NULL, 'Heal - Sister (Original Mix)<br />\r\nHeal - Sister (Amarilyo Remix)<br />\r\nHeal - Sister (Deepstereo Remix)<br />\r\nHeal - Sister (Maxim Play Remix)', 1, '2016-05-20 15:53:09', '2016-05-20 15:53:09'),
