(1559, 237, 'CTStreams EP vol. 6', 'CTS237133', '2013-08-16', '1559_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/ctstreams-vol-6/1141735', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'Sixth edition of CTStreams is focused on underground side. Tech and minimal, intelligent, deep and dark but also pumping and funky shades as well are presented by Tim Deetakt, Dee Mares and Second Stage, each track tells a story.. dance with the sound of the underground...', NULL, NULL, 'Dee Mares - System Error<br />\r\nTim Deetakt - Divine Rhinoceros<br />\r\nSecond Stage - Weightlessness', 1, '2016-05-20 16:07:17', '2016-05-20 16:07:17'),
