(1577, 245, 'Yan Oxygen - Solio EP', 'CTS245133', '2013-12-13', '1577_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/yan-oxygen-solio-ep/1212479', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'Well known techno DJ &amp; producer Yan Oxygen submits three new powerfull tracks in his Solio EP. All of them are &nbsp;impregnated with old school flavour. Strong and tight big room techno sound will drive the dancefloor crazy... explosive ride!', NULL, NULL, 'Yan Oxygen - Solio<br />\r\nYan Oxygen - Kaleidoscope<br />\r\nYan Oxygen - I Can&acute;t Control it', 1, '2016-05-20 15:22:55', '2016-05-20 15:22:55'),
(1580, 246, 'Sergio Mega - Deeper Dnieper EP', 'CTS246133', '2013-12-17', '1580_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/sergio-mega-deeper-dnieper/1215804', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'New tech-house single by Sergio Mega is made with flavour of deep and jazzy influences. Solo keyboard improvise is supplemented with fluent chords and &nbsp;sinuous waved bass, all the details on their places creates a mood of the tune. Also coming atmospheric remix by &nbsp;Californian duo Heal, groovy, deep and techy remix by Pablo Caballero from Argentina and soft acid jazz remix by Kiruchell.. dancing in the deep snow...', NULL, NULL, 'Sergio Mega - Deeper Dnieper (Original Mix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega - Deeper Dnieper (Heal Remix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega - Deeper Dnieper (Kirunchell Remix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega - Deeper Dnieper (Pablo Caballero Remix)', 1, '2016-05-20 15:19:55', '2016-05-20 15:19:55'),
(1581, 247, 'Sergio Mega - Opening EP', 'CTS247133', '2013-12-20', '1581_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/sergio-mega-opening/1215810', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'Another single by Sergio Mega continue house and deep theme. Groovy house and deep original mix made with shades of tech-house. Chords and melodic intonation takes into the shining atmosphere of party red line somewhere in Paris. Tuny house Remix by Buckle Up! Records label boss Duart Jansen vs. North &amp; Funk from the Netherlads characterized with vibrating bassline and influeces of nu disco. Kirunchell submits tight slow deep house sound with jazzy vibes.. party begins!...', NULL, NULL, 'Sergio Mega - Opening (Original Mix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega - Opening (Kirunchell Remix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega - Opening (Duart Jansen vs. North &amp; Funk Mix)', 1, '2016-05-20 14:53:09', '2016-05-20 14:53:09'),
