(1600, 254, 'THE BEST TRANCE IN UA (VOL.4)', 'CTS254143', '2014-01-24', '1600_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/the-best-trance-in-ua-vol-4/1232751', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'CTS Records presents the best Trance tracks of the year by Ukrainian producers.', NULL, NULL, 'Alexey Kuznetsov - Dialog<br />\r\nAmind Two Guys - Dream Night<br />\r\nAmind Two Guys - Eternity<br />\r\nAndy Groove ft. Asheria &amp; Julia Lav - Night Stations<br />\r\nDJ Dimmy Way - When a Sun is Replaced by Lunar<br />\r\nGeorge Gee - We Are<br />\r\nRadana - Walk of Imagination<br />\r\nSluice - Birthday<br />\r\nState4 - New Day, New Discoverings<br />\r\nTim Lighterz - Summer Fresh<br />\r\nViktor Dance - Step to Harmony<br />\r\nVitaliy Shot - Green Peace<br />\r\nVyacheslav Demchenko - My Marvellous Dream', 1, '2016-05-20 14:24:11', '2016-05-20 14:24:11'),
(1602, 255, 'DIGITALmusikanten - Tripping ', 'CTS255143', '2014-01-31', '1602_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/tripping/1236640', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'New single &quot;Tripping&quot; by German duo DIGITALmusikanten is out at CTS in January. Tech-house original mix made with groovy bassline and unobtrusive vocal parts. The release is coming with atmospheric remix by Heal, tight and techy edit by Pablo Caballero and two deep house mixes by Neopoly Project and Rousing.. hang up and dance!...', NULL, NULL, 'DIGITALmusikanten - Tripping (Original Mix)<br />\r\nDIGITALmusikanten - Tripping (Heal Remix)<br />\r\nDIGITALmusikanten - Tripping (Rousing Remix)<br />\r\nDIGITALmusikanten - Tripping (Pablo Caballero Remix)<br />\r\nDIGITALmusikanten - Tripping (Neopoly Project Remix)', 1, '2016-05-20 14:20:47', '2016-05-20 14:20:47'),
(1605, 256, 'CTSpeakers EP vol.1', 'CTS256143', '2014-02-14', '1605_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/ctspeakers-ep-vol-1/1244615', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'In 2014 like each new year CTS Records traditionally begin new EP series. Three new deep house and nu disco tracks are made for first edition of CTSpeakers. Touch My Hand by Monovakzin with vocoder and synth elements, Time Machine bu Oleg Stuff with disco influences and soft deep tune by Rousing completes the release...', NULL, NULL, 'Monovakzin - Touch My Hand<br />\r\nOleg Stuff - Time Machine<br />\r\nRousing - One Way Ticket', 1, '2016-05-20 14:18:11', '2016-05-20 14:18:11'),
(1606, 257, 'Voltereto - Funky Train', 'CTS257143', '2014-02-21', '1606_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/voltereto-funky-train/1250206', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'We are welcome Voltereto with Funky Train release on CTS Records. Experienced house artist from Spain, more then 30 years of DJing, deliver 122 bpm groovy house banger. Disco flavored remix by Oleg Stuff, atmospheric deep house edit by Neopoly Project and Amarilyo added hot filtered vibes to his house remix mixture.. take a ride it&acute;s Funky Train!...', NULL, NULL, 'Voltereto - Funky Train (Original Mix)<br />\r\nVoltereto - Funky Train (Amarilyo Remix)<br />\r\nVoltereto - Funky Train (Oleg Stuff Remix)<br />\r\nVoltereto - Funky Train (Neopoly Project Remix)', 1, '2016-05-20 14:16:40', '2016-05-20 14:16:40'),
(1609, 258, 'Mute Solo - Endorphine', 'CTS258143', '2014-03-04', '1609_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/mute-solo-endorphine/1257034', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'Single release by Mute Solo is one more reminder that CTS loves Techno sound. Atonal elements are coming through the all mixes, Original is tight and strong, Re-Dub is more focused on synth line, Oxy Beat submit groovy and hypnotic edit, and Ilisho Group comes with deep and slow vibes...', NULL, NULL, 'Mute Solo - Endorphine (Original Mix)<br />\r\nMute Solo - Endorphine (Ilisho Group Remix)<br />\r\nMute Solo - Endorphine (Oxy Beat Remix)<br />\r\nMute Solo - Endorphine (Re-Dub)', 1, '2016-05-18 15:47:29', '2016-05-18 15:47:29'),
(1611, 259, 'struCTS vol.11', 'CTS259143', '2014-03-14', '1611_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/structs-11/1263703', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'Elevens StruCTS compilation is deep Housey and Techy suplemented with atmospheric Chill Out and hypnotic Prog tunes. Selection of tracks by Yan Oxygen, Sergio Mega, Heal, Yuri Petrovski, DIGITALmusikanten, Artemy Cheros, BBM 2, Alexey Kuznetsov, DJ Kot, Frozen, Masse &nbsp;with remixes by Deepstereo, Kain and also Rousing... Play them loud...', '', NULL, 'Yuri Petrovski -&nbsp;Pretty Lights&nbsp;(Original Mix) DIGITALmusikanten -&nbsp;Tripping (Rousing Remix)<br />\r\nArtemy Cheros -&nbsp;&nbsp;Funky Drop&nbsp;(Original Mix)<br />\r\nBBM II -&nbsp;Dakota 08&nbsp;(Original Mix)<br />\r\nAlexey Kuznetsov -&nbsp;Shaman (Original Mix)<br />\r\nYan Oxygen -&nbsp;I Can&acute;t Contol It&nbsp;(Original Mix)<br />\r\nAlexey Kuznetsov -&nbsp;Oceano&nbsp;(Original Mix)<br />\r\nDJ KoT -&nbsp;Digital Mind Analog Soul&nbsp;(Original Mix)<br />\r\nHeal -&nbsp;Sister (Deepstereo Remix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega -&nbsp;Vagator (Kain Remix)<br />\r\nFrozen -&nbsp;Mad Glue&nbsp;(Original Mix)<br />\r\nMasse -&nbsp;Bass Is Angry&nbsp;(Original Mix)', 1, '2016-09-20 12:58:00', '2016-09-20 12:58:00'),
(1612, 260, 'Sergio Mega - Ornamental (the Album)', 'CTS260143', '2014-03-21', '1612_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/sergio-mega-ornamental-the-album/1269124', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'The third album of Sergio Mega &quot;Ornamental&quot; comes out in the spring of 2014. Name of the album consists of two volumetric components, which means Ornament - DNA of the nation and Mentality - the soul of the nation. The release concept is coupled global authentic culture and modern electronic music. The project includes eleven audio pieces; each one is based on musical traditions from around the world, combining their rich texture with rhythmic electronic instruments and synthesizers. Remixes for the album tracks except Ukrainian sound producers already made by the artists from the United States, Spain, Argentina, Germany, Malta, Italy, the Netherlands and Mexico as well. The main objective of the project show colors Ukrainian musical culture an integral part of the global palette ornament. As a result, the integration of Ukrainian electronic sound into the flow of international contemporary electronic music.', NULL, NULL, 'Sergio Mega -&nbsp;Opening (Original Mix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega -&nbsp;Vagator&nbsp;(Original Mix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega -&nbsp;Stereoland (Ornamental Mix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega - Upper&nbsp;(Original Mix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega &nbsp;- Carnaval (Album Version)<br />\r\nSergio Mega -&nbsp;Gogol&nbsp;(Original Mix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega -&nbsp;Kyiv Skies&nbsp;(Original Mix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega - Mystic &amp; Wilde (Album Version)<br />\r\nSergio Mega -&nbsp;Deeper Dnieper&nbsp;(Original Mix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega feat. Jean Osoa&nbsp;-&nbsp;In Motion (Original Mix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega -&nbsp;Beat On The Drums&nbsp;(Original Mix)', 1, '2016-05-18 15:40:40', '2016-05-18 15:40:40'),
(1615, 261, 'Simon Spencer - Hold On to Me EP', 'CTS261143', '2014-03-28', '1615_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/simon-spencer-hold-on-to-me-ep/1272228', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'CTS Records presents Italian talent who keep the ballance between deep house and tech house - Simon Spencer with new EP Hold On to Me. Three tracks melodic and atmospheric are dark and light in same time. Groovy tunes with different shades of deep house and nu disco sound are flavored with vocoder voices and analog style synths.. peace, love, music, no war...', NULL, NULL, 'Simon Spencer -&nbsp;A la Plage<br />\r\nSimon Spencer -&nbsp;Hold On to Me<br />\r\nSimon Spencer -&nbsp;Do You Know Do You Feel', 1, '2016-05-18 15:37:20', '2016-05-18 15:37:20'),
(1618, 262, 'CTSpeakers EP vol.2', 'CTS262143', '2014-04-18', '1618_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/ctspeakers-ep-vol-2/1287873', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'Next CTSpeakers EP presents different shades of House music. Deep and atmospheric &quot;Merkaba&quot; by Amarilyo &amp; Peter Und Der Wolf is supplemented with live sax parts, &quot;Do Not Stop&quot; with old school moods and nu dico syhnth by DJ Chiff and &quot;Mirage in the Clouds&quot; by Vialii Sky is deep and dark.. connect, dive and enjoy...', NULL, NULL, 'Amarilyo &amp; Peter Und Der Wolf<br />\r\nDJ Chif&nbsp;&nbsp;- Do Not Stop&nbsp;&nbsp;- Merkaba<br />\r\nVialii Sky&nbsp;&nbsp;- Mirage in the Clouds', 1, '2016-05-18 15:34:48', '2016-05-18 15:34:48'),
(1620, 263, 'Terry Raze - Our Life', 'CTS2643143', '2014-04-25', '1620_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/terry-raze-our-life-ep/1291446', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'With his next personal EP on CTS Terry Raze deliver deep and tech house sound in three brand new tracks. Glitch and syncopic vibes where is a space for air. &quot;Suflet&quot; with solid intro and liquid atmospheric pads could be good as a set starter, T.V.O.N. is tight and groovy as well as as &quot;Our life&quot; which is supplemented with looped vocal layer... deep and strong... Enjoy', NULL, NULL, 'Terry Raze -&nbsp;Suflet<br />\r\nTerry Raze -&nbsp;Our Life<br />\r\nTerry Raze T.V.O.N.', 1, '2016-05-18 15:33:14', '2016-05-18 15:33:14'),
(1622, 264, 'CTSpeakers EP vol.3', 'CTS264143', '2014-05-02', '1622_s.jpg', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/ctspeakers-ep-vol-3/1295911', 'With third CTSpeakers EP CTS deliver differnt shades of techno sound. Melodic and atmospheric &quot;Temptation&quot; by Roman Sweet, transparent and hypnotic &quot;Napoli&quot; by Jaroslaw and dirty and noisy Pathfinger by Teoss.. Make your choice...', NULL, NULL, 'Jaroslaw - Napoli<br />\r\nTeoss - Pathfinger<br />\r\nRoman Sweet - Temptation', 1, '2016-05-18 15:30:05', '2016-05-18 15:30:05'),
(1624, 265, 'Sergio Mega - One Eight', 'CTS265143', '2014-05-16', '1624_s.jpg', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/sergio-mega-one-eight/1302669', 'New single &quot;One Eight&quot; by Sergio Mega is coming out at CTS Records.<br />\r\nDeep 118 bpm Original mix with nu disco shades is supplemented with tight tech house remix by Mamay and soft and slow deep house mix by Adeseyo.. Enjoy', NULL, NULL, 'Sergio Mega - One Eight (Original Mix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega - One Eight (Mamay Mix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega - One Eight (AdeseyoMix)', 1, '2016-05-18 15:28:27', '2016-05-18 15:28:27'),
(1626, 266, 'CTSpeakers EP vol.4', 'CTS266143', '2014-05-23', '1626_s.jpg', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/ctspeakers-ep-vol-4/1304906', 'As usual three new tracks are coming out in CTSpeakers EP. Endorphin by Vitalii Sky and Survivor by Carmelo Carone both based on acid, and slow tech joint Magnet with shades of old schhol sound by Technolog...', '', NULL, 'Vitalii Sky - Endorphin<br />\r\nTechnolog - Magnet<br />\r\nCarmelo Carone - Survivor', 1, '2016-08-12 11:18:18', '2016-08-12 11:18:18'),
(1628, 267, 'Monovakzin - Monothalamus EP', 'CTS267143', '2014-05-30', '1628_s.jpg', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/monovakzin-monothalamus-ep/1312959', 'Monovakzin deliver light sounds in deep house esthetic with shades of nu disco. Both tracks &quot;Monothalamus&quot; and &quot;Basic Process&quot; are full of summer moods supplemented with analog synth parts and old school rhythm vibes... Enjoy', NULL, NULL, 'Monovakzin -&nbsp;Monothalamus<br />\r\nMonovakzin -&nbsp;Basic Process', 1, '2016-05-18 15:23:16', '2016-05-18 15:23:16'),
(1630, 268, 'INME - Baby Now EP', 'CTS268143', '2014-06-13', '1630_s.jpg', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/inme-baby-now-ep/1321450', 'CTS continue presentation of Ukrainian electronic music talents. After the winning The Best Track in Ukraine progressive nomination, Alex Love turn his skills to house side. As a result brand new EP with shades of old school house and UK garage touch is out under Alex Love&acute;s house &amp; deep alias INME...', NULL, NULL, 'INME - Baby Now (Original Mix)<br />\r\nINME - Can You&nbsp;(Original Mix)', 1, '2016-05-18 15:20:23', '2016-05-18 15:20:23'),
(1633, 269, 'CTSPEAKERS EP VOL.5', 'CTS269143', '2014-06-27', '1633_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/ctspeakers-ep-vol-5/1329671', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'With fifth CTSpeakers EP CTS deliver sound for summer relaxation. Three new downtempo, chill out and electronica tracks with mysterious mystical moods, excellent for horizontal dancing... feel the magic touch...', NULL, NULL, 'Ikiro -&nbsp;KORFF (Original Mix)<br />\r\nOtto Sigma -&nbsp;Tuomionpaivan Jalkeen (Original Mix)<br />\r\nSlava Yaroslavskiy -&nbsp;Abstract (Original Mix)', 1, '2016-05-18 15:17:51', '2016-05-18 15:17:51'),
(1635, 270, 'Sketch of Groove - Paris EP', 'CTS270143', '2014-07-18', '1635_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/sketch-of-groove-paris-ep/1342927', 'http://www.cts-label.com/beatport.html', 'Another chill out EP is coming out on CTS Records. Two new acid jazz tracks with smooth lines, soft vibes and pleasant feeling of excitement by Sketch of Groove...', NULL, NULL, 'Sketch of Groove - Paris<br />\r\nSketch of Groove - Moloko', 1, '2016-05-18 15:14:53', '2016-05-18 15:14:53'),
(1637, 271, 'struCTS vol.12', 'CTS271143', '2014-07-25', '1637_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/structs-12/1345718', 'www.beatport.com/label/cts-creative-technologies-studio/4470', 'Twelfth StruCTS compilation is mostly about nu disco and deep house with inclusions of tech house and techno. Selection of tracks by Sergio Mega, Simon Spencer, Terry Raze, Vitalii Sky, RezQ Sound, Roman Sweet and remix made by Mamay. Tracks of this selection are supported by DJs from all the continents around the globe except perhaps the Antarctica... One Eight by Sergio Mega has reached first place in DJ Barometer music chart.. play them loud...', '', NULL, 'Sergio Mega -&nbsp;One Eight (Original Mix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega -&nbsp;One Eight (Mamay Remix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega -&nbsp;Stereoland (Ornamental Mix)<br />\r\nSimon Spencer -&nbsp;A la Plage&nbsp;(Original Mix)<br />\r\nSimon Spencer -&nbsp;Hold On to Me&nbsp;(Original Mix)<br />\r\nTerry Raze -&nbsp;Suflet&nbsp;(Original Mix)<br />\r\nTerry Raze -&nbsp;T.V.O.N.&nbsp;(Original Mix)<br />\r\nVitalii Sky -&nbsp;Mirage in the Clouds&nbsp;(Original Mix)<br />\r\nRezQ Sound -&nbsp;Chasm&nbsp;(Original Mix)<br />\r\nRoman Sweet -&nbsp;Temptation&nbsp;(Original Mix)', 1, '2016-09-20 12:57:51', '2016-09-20 12:57:51');
