(1639, 272, 'TIM DEETAKT - MOONSTONE EP', 'CTS272143', '2014-08-29', '1639_s.jpg', 'www.beatport.com/label/cts-creative-technologies-studio/4470', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/tim-deetakt-moonstone-ep/1367552', 'Dutch dj &amp; producer Tim Deetakt deliver deep and dark underground sound with his Moonstone EP. Original and Techouse mixes of the Moonstone are suplemented with tight and spiny Savhas.. Enjoy', NULL, NULL, 'Tim Deetakt -&nbsp;Moonstone (Original Mix)<br />\r\nTim Deetakt -&nbsp;Moonstone (Techouse Mix)<br />\r\nTim Deetakt -&nbsp;Savhas (Original Mix)', 1, '2016-05-18 15:07:57', '2016-05-18 15:07:57'),
(1641, 273, 'ALEKSANDR LIFE - SALT SHAKER', 'CTS273143', '2014-09-05', '1641_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/aleksandr-life-salt-shaker/1371982', 'http://www.beatport.com/label/cts-creative-technologies-studio/4470', 'New release Salt Shaker by Aleksandr Life is made between Techno and Tech House. Stright and tight original with 909 shades is suplemented with Dub mix which is more syncopic and percussive. Both mixes are groovy dancefloor killers, make your choice.. Enjoy...', NULL, NULL, 'Aleksandr Life - Salt Shaker (Original Mix)<br />\r\nAleksandr Life - Salt Shaker (Dub Mix)', 1, '2016-05-18 15:04:24', '2016-05-18 15:04:24'),
(1643, 274, 'CTSpeakers EP vol.6', 'CTS274143', '2014-09-19', '1643_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/label/cts-creative-technologies-studio/4470', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/ctspeakers-ep-vol-6/1379954', 'New CTSpeakers EP is coming out with nu disco, deep house and chill out sound inside. Step by Step by Oleg Stuff fits for 2000th break dance soundtrack and live improvise with soft bassline in Midnight Samurai by Kirunchell...', NULL, NULL, 'Kirunchell -&nbsp;Midnight Samurai&nbsp;(Original Mix)<br />\r\nOleg Stuff -&nbsp;Step by Step&nbsp;(Original Mix)', 1, '2016-05-18 15:00:14', '2016-05-18 15:00:14'),
(1645, 275, 'Yuriy Berliny - Cosmopolis EP', 'CTS275143', '2014-09-26', '1645_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/yuriy-berliny-cosmopolis-ep/1384946', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/yuriy-berliny-cosmopolis-ep/1384946', 'Yuriy Berliny deliver deep and atmospheric mixture of techo, tech-house and chill-out. Groovy rhythmic forms with minimal influences are supplemented with transparent vocal parts. Great for dancing and for listening as well.. do what you like...', '', NULL, 'Yuriy Berliny &nbsp;- Cosmopolis (Original Mix)<br />\r\nYuriy Berliny -&nbsp;Free Your Mind (Original Mix)<br />\r\nYuriy Berliny -&nbsp;Wild Wolf (Original Mix)', 1, '2016-09-14 10:38:43', '2016-09-14 10:38:43'),
(1647, 276, 'Sergio Mega - Bicycle Day', 'CTS276143', '2014-10-03', '1647_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/label/cts-creative-technologies-studio/4470', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/sergio-mega-bicycle-day/1389666', 'New release by Sergio Mega is made with disco influences and dedicated to the sound which opened minds of new generations for the modern understanding of dance music. Analog synths and vintage drums works well for the groove. Nu disco Original and Dub mixes are supplemented with hypnotic deep house remix by Deepstereo and tight techno mix with shades of German school electro by Electreefication duo... open your eyes...', NULL, NULL, 'Sergio Mega - Bicycle Day (Original vocal mix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega - Bicycle Day (Dub mix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega - Bicycle Day (Deepstereo remix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega - Bicycle Day (Electreefication remix)', 1, '2016-05-18 14:54:37', '2016-05-18 14:54:37'),
(1648, 277, 'Monovakzin - Trafficker EP', 'CTS277143', '2014-10-10', '1648_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/label/cts-creative-technologies-studio/4470', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/monovakzin-trafficker-ep/1394110', 'It&acute;s our pleasure to announce new outstanding EP by Monovakzin at CTS! Two Deep House and nu disco tracks are influenced with UK underground house sound esthetics, also have their own fresh colour. Soft beats of Inrail with screaming disco vocals are supplemented with tight and eclectic Trafficker - dancefloor killer!', NULL, NULL, 'Monovakzin - In Rail (Original Mix)<br />\r\nMonovakzin -&nbsp;Traffickerm (Original Mix)', 1, '2016-05-18 14:52:14', '2016-05-18 14:52:14'),
(1651, 278, 'Dog Off - Robotics', 'CTS278143', '2014-11-07', '1651_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/label/cts-creative-technologies-studio/4470', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/dog-off-robotics/1411436', 'Deep, extraordinary long-awaited release by Dog Off Robotics is coming out now. Unexpected twists of the extended mix are supplemented with two deep remixes light air structures by Amarilyo and dark, atmospheric groovy joint by Heal with soft bassline and penetrating sweeps.. plunge into sounds...', NULL, NULL, 'Dog Off - Robotics (Extended Mix)<br />\r\nDog Off - Robotics (Amarilyo Remix)<br />\r\nDog Off - Robotics (Heal Remix)', 1, '2016-05-18 14:49:25', '2016-05-18 14:49:25'),
(1653, 279, 'INME - What I Feel EP', 'CTS279143', '2014-11-21', '1653_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/label/cts-creative-technologies-studio/4470', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/inme-what-i-feel-ep/1419927', 'Two tight and hot tunes by INME are coming out on CTS. Both vocal house tracks with piano parts and groovy bassline. Pumping and funky &quot;What I Feel&quot; plus atmospheric and soulful &quot;What to Do&quot; compile explosive mixture.. enjoy', NULL, NULL, 'INME -&nbsp;What I Feel&nbsp;(Original Mix)<br />\r\nINME -&nbsp;What to Do&nbsp;(Original Mix)', 1, '2016-05-18 14:46:13', '2016-05-18 14:46:13'),
(1654, 280, 'Tough Stuff - Trans Me', 'CTS290143', '2014-12-12', '1654_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/label/cts-creative-technologies-studio/4470', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/tough-stuff-trans-me/1434347', 'Another deep and tech house release is coming out at CTS Records. Trans Me by Tough Stuff is groovy and deep, original mix is supplemented with delicious nu disco influenced atmospheric deep house remix by Moe Turk and tight tech house Lee Webster&acute;s Yummy Legs Remix... Enjoy!...', NULL, NULL, 'Tough Stuff - Trans Me (Original Mix)<br />\r\nTough Stuff - Trans Me (Lee Webster&acute;s Yummy Legs Remix)<br />\r\nTough Stuff - Trans Me (Moe Turk Remix)', 1, '2016-05-18 14:46:41', '2016-05-18 14:46:41'),
(1657, 281, 'CTSmashers Part 7', 'CTS291143', '2014-12-26', '1657_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/label/cts-creative-technologies-studio/4470', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/ctsmashers-part-7/1441709', 'In 2014 CTS celebrates 10 years anniversary. In honor of this event two compilations are coming out. CTSmashers 7 is dedicated to house sound. Groovy and atmospheric, with shades of deep and elements of nu disco that is so characteristic for CTS recently...', NULL, NULL, 'Dog Off - Robotics (Amarilyo Remix)<br />\r\nKirunchell - Midnight Samurai (Original Mix)<br />\r\nTough Stuff - Trans Me (Moe Turk Remix)<br />\r\nKomplektov - Fickle Temper&nbsp;(Original Mix)<br />\r\nSimon Spencer - A la Plage&nbsp;(Original Mix)<br />\r\nDIGITALmusikanten - Tripping (Rousing Remix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega - One Eight (Adeseyo Remix)<br />\r\nMaxim Play - Spring Snow&nbsp;(Original Mix)<br />\r\nHeal - Sister (Deepstereo Remix)<br />\r\nINME - Baby Now (Original Mix)<br />\r\nTerry Raze - Suflet&nbsp;(Original Mix)<br />\r\nYuriy Berliny - Cosmopolis&nbsp;(Original Mix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega - Deeper Dnieper (Original Mix)<br />\r\nYuri Petrovski - Pretty Lights (Original Mix)', 1, '2016-05-18 14:47:08', '2016-05-18 14:47:08'),
(1659, 282, 'CTSmashers Part 8', 'CTS282143', '2014-12-30', '1659_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/label/cts-creative-technologies-studio/4470', 'http://www.beatport.com/release/ctsmashers-part-8/1441710', 'Being traditional faithful to techno sound, CTS dedicate part 8 of CTSmashers 10 years anniversary compilation to Techno. Dark, deep and trippy mixture of highest rated CTS techno and tech-house tracks of 2014 is selected here.', NULL, NULL, 'DJ KoT - Digital Mind Analog Soul&nbsp;(Original Mix)<br />\r\nNeopoly Project - The Dance of the Dark&nbsp;(Original Mix)<br />\r\nAlexey Kuznetsov - Shaman&nbsp;(Original Mix)<br />\r\nJaroslaw - Napoli&nbsp;(Original Mix)<br />\r\nAleksandr Life - Salt Shaker (Dub Mix)<br />\r\nRezQ Sound - Chasm&nbsp;(Original Mix)<br />\r\nAleksandr Life - Salt Shaker (Original Mix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega - One Eight (Mamay Remix)<br />\r\nTim Deetakt - Savhas (Original Mix)<br />\r\nYan Oxygen - I Can&acute;t Contol It&nbsp;(Original Mix)<br />\r\nYuri Petrovski - Deep Breath&nbsp;(Original Mix)', 1, '2016-05-17 12:19:55', '2016-05-17 12:19:55'),
