(1671, 286, 'Vitalii Sky - Acid Swing EP', 'CTS286153', '2015-01-23', '1671_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/label/cts-creative-technologies-studio/4470', 'https://pro.beatport.com/release/acid-swing-ep/1453334', 'You&lsquo;d like to refresh your set with old school beats and acid vibes? Here you are! Vitalii Sky deliver two trippy old school influenced acid productions, both are deep and dark with well recognizable all time bassline sounds... Enjoy', NULL, NULL, 'Vitalii Sky - Acid Swing (Original Mix)<br />\r\nVitalii Sky - City Dance Rhythms of Acid&nbsp;(Original Mix)', 1, '2016-05-17 11:59:45', '2016-05-17 11:59:45'),
