(1677, 289, 'Sergio Mega - Moving Part 1', 'CTS289153', '2015-02-13', '1677_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/label/cts-creative-technologies-studio/4470', 'https://pro.beatport.com/release/moving-part-1/1455323', 'Moving by Sergio Mega is coming out on CTS. Original mix spiced with vocoder and analog synths parts is supplemented with groovy Deepstereo remix with deep chords and sweeps. Amarilyo deliver nu disco rework with soft keys and pads influenced with old school disco vibes as well.. moving up!', '', NULL, 'Sergio Mega - Moving (Original Mix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega - Moving (Amarilyo Remix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega - Moving (Deepstereo Remix)', 1, '2016-11-22 14:29:45', '2016-11-22 14:29:45'),
