(1683, 292, 'Seventeenth Unvrse - Me & I Corrupted EP', 'Seventeenth Unvrse - Me & I Corrupted EP', '2015-03-30', '1683_s.jpg', 'http://www.beatport.com/label/cts-creative-technologies-studio/4470', 'https://pro.beatport.com/release/seventeenth-unvrse-me-and-i-corrupted-ep/1498792#', 'After Avicii contest winning and the winning of two nominations in the Best track in Ukraine contest, Kiss FM choice and the Main Prize, Haxxy didn&lsquo;t sit on one&lsquo;s hands. Productive author of a new formation, shows one more his side and opens for electronic music lovers his another alter ego Seventeenth Unvrse. First EP of the project will coming out on CTS Records in March. Dedicated to underground deep house, deep techno and tech-house, sound of the Seventeenth Unvrse is very musical and harmonic as it is characteristic to Ukrainian prodcer. Open minded sound find a new horizon for the new wave authors creative work.. Dark and full of unexpected turns with revenant vocal inclusions both tracks of the EP reflects an authors position for his new alter ego. Haxxy says: &quot;Project Seventeenth Unvrse - is the fruit (result) of my oscillation between melody and rigor in the tracks, directed to work towards melodic techno music&quot; EP is opens with hypnotic intro of the &quot;Dirty Love&quot; with analog lead and soft bassline triplet vibes. &quot;Me &amp; I Corrupted&quot; is bit more tight, accent there is moved more to the rhythm, but still transparent, emotional and atmospheric&hellip; welcome to the next level&hellip; stay tuned...', NULL, NULL, 'Seventeenth Unvrse - Dirty Love<br />\r\nSeventeenth Unvrse - Me &amp; I Corrupted', 1, '2016-05-16 16:14:38', '2016-05-16 16:14:38'),
(1685, 293, 'Sergio Mega - Moving Part 2', 'CTS293153', '2015-04-10', '1685_s.jpg', 'https://pro.beatport.com/release/moving-part-2/1509481', 'https://pro.beatport.com/release/moving-part-2/1509481', 'Second part of Moving release by Sergio Mega is focused mostly on Nu Disco sound. Otto Sigma Remix with bit dirty bassline ans smoth synth parts shows remixers adherence to Synth Wave music. Saskin S Disco Remix is based on rich Disco traditions and full of soft, warm vintage parts. Matt Moore deliver Tech House remix tight and groovy.. make your choice and move your way...', NULL, NULL, 'Sergio Mega - Moving ((Matt Moore Remix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega - Moving (Otto Sigma Remix)<br />\r\nSergio Mega - Moving (Saskin S Disco Remix)', 1, '2016-05-16 16:10:13', '2016-05-16 16:10:13'),
