(1688, 295, 'CTSpaces EP vol.1', 'CTS295153', '2015-04-24', '1688_s.jpg', 'https://pro.beatport.com/release/ctspaces-ep-vol-1/1518346', 'https://pro.beatport.com/release/ctspaces-ep-vol-1/1518346', 'Traditionally each year CTS releases new EP series. &nbsp;For 2015 CTS launches a brand new concept with new art work design CTSpaces but despite the new look it will be directed as usual to the sound which is characteristic to CTS. Techno and house are as before the predominant line for the label. For the first CTSpaces EP were choosed atmospheric deep house track &quot;There is Not Reality in Reality&quot; bu Vitalii Sky, trippy tech-house and deep tune &quot;Kenna&quot; by Unheal also as a good supplement techno deep and acid &quot;Tamborero&quot; track by &nbsp;Sweep Project duo from Chile...', '', NULL, 'Sweep Projekt - Tamborero<br />\r\nUnheal - Kanna<br />\r\nVitalii SkY - There is Not Reality in Reality', 1, '2016-09-19 11:26:33', '2016-09-19 11:26:33'),
