(1692, 297, 'Dasero - Eclipse EP', 'CTS297153', '2015-05-22', '1692_s.jpg', 'https://pro.beatport.com/release/dasero-eclipse-ep/1536932', 'https://pro.beatport.com/release/dasero-eclipse-ep/1536932', 'We are glad to introduce London based muty genre artist Dasero with Eclips EP on CTS Records. On this release Dasero is focused in deep tech-house and techno sound. &quot;Deepflow&quot; solid &nbsp;tech groove track is spiced with dark and deep chords, bit more housy atmospheric &quot;Nightlights&quot; is tight and groovy as weel, both works are united by original vocal processing. Title track of the release tech house production &quot;Eclips&quot; with syncopic bassline is supplemented with IDM elements...', NULL, NULL, 'Dasero - Deepflow<br />\r\nDasero - Eclipse<br />\r\nDasero - Nightlights', 1, '2016-05-16 16:04:44', '2016-05-16 16:04:44'),
(1694, 298, 'Otto Sigma - Technoisle EP', 'CTS298153', '2015-05-29', '1694_s.jpg', 'https://pro.beatport.com/release/otto-sigma-technoisle-ep/1540878', 'https://pro.beatport.com/release/otto-sigma-technoisle-ep/1540878', 'With Technoisle EP Otto Sigma deliver new look to disco sound, retro elements, synth and drum parts, are framed in modern groove. All three instrumental tracks are made with vintage touch. Warm melodic sounding have also good dance punch... enjoy<br />', NULL, NULL, 'Otto Sigma - 8dc<br />\r\nOtto Sigma - Rotation Matrix<br />\r\nOtto Sigma - Technoisle (Extended Mix)<br />\r\nOtto Sigma - Technoisle (Original Mix)', 1, '2016-05-16 16:03:43', '2016-05-16 16:03:43'),
(1696, 299, 'Demophon Muson - Want To Know', 'CTS299153', '2015-06-19', '1696_s.jpg', 'https://pro.beatport.com/release/demophon-muson-want-to-know/1553395', 'https://pro.beatport.com/release/demophon-muson-want-to-know/1553395', 'Following the recent successful premiere of the original version of the video Want To Know, the Demophon Muson band members met with Ukrainian DJ and producer Sergio Mega. As a result, a new project come in sight - the continuation of a video story about finding yourself and answer the main questions. Sergio Mega, known for his work for the dance scene made the remix for Want To Know. The joint work of all participants showed character of the both, guitar passages and the vocals, which fully comply with the original song has supplemented with electronic groove. &quot;Rock and electronics have always been interesting to me no less than the dance music, techno and house. Indie in conjunction with the Deep, in my opinion, very good-looking connection. In addition, I am impressed by the position, as well as philosophical and creative search of Demophon Muson guys, so I took up the project. In my remix I tried to keep hot attitude and expression, pronounced in the original track, and from myself I have added the dance vibrations, rhythms and melancholy that is characteristic for modern Ukrainian electronic sound&quot;, - says Sergio Mega.', NULL, NULL, 'Demophon Muson - Want To Know (Sergio Mega Remix)', 1, '2016-05-16 16:01:50', '2016-05-16 16:01:50'),
(1698, 300, 'struCTS vol.13', 'CTS300153', '2015-07-03', '1698_s.jpg', 'https://pro.beatport.com/release/structs-vol-13/1565162', 'https://pro.beatport.com/release/structs-vol-13/1565162', '13th edition of struCTS compilation is mostly focused on different shades of house and techno. Trippy, deep and punchy vibes are spiced with nu disco and electronica sound... Enjoy', '', NULL, 'Sergio Mega - Movig (Saskin S Disco remix)<br />\r\nSweep Projekt &nbsp;- Tamborero &nbsp;<br />\r\nTough Stuff &ndash; Trans Me (Lee Webster&rsquo;s Yummy Legs Remix)<br />\r\nHaxxy &ndash; End of the world &nbsp;<br />\r\nVitalii Sky &ndash; City dance of Rhythms of acid&nbsp;<br />\r\nPauly &ndash; Red Twin&nbsp;<br />\r\nRiolie &ndash; Bewilderment&nbsp;<br />\r\nSlackers Project, Pirania &ndash; BOOM&nbsp;<br />\r\nRisepunk - &nbsp;Waiting for you&nbsp;<br />\r\nSergio Mega &ndash; Moving &nbsp;(Matt Moore remix)<br />\r\ndENNYSunShine &ndash; Oxiomma (NidsheDeLuxe)&nbsp;<br />\r\nSergio Mega &ndash; Moving (Original Mix)<br />\r\nMasse &ndash; Suspenders (Club Mix)<br />\r\nTerry Raze &ndash; LightRoom&nbsp;<br />\r\nSergio Mega &ndash; Moving (Amarilyo Remix)<br />\r\nIgor Graphite - &nbsp;Labirynth &nbsp;<br />\r\nVitalli Sky &ndash; Acid Swing<br />\r\nMasse &ndash; Kiss piano rol&nbsp;<br />\r\nRiolie &ndash; Lady on the bridge&nbsp;<br />\r\nVitamindevil &ndash; Keep out&nbsp;', 1, '2016-09-20 12:57:42', '2016-09-20 12:57:42'),
(1704, 301, 'INME & 8.30AM - Bustling Space ', 'CTS301153', '2015-07-24', '1704_s.jpg', 'https://pro.beatport.com/release/bustling-space/1575184', 'https://pro.beatport.com/release/bustling-space/1575184', 'For the Bustling Space release INME and 8.30 AM prepared hot mixture in their studio. House and deep with old school drum elements, real life noise textures and dark voxes. Terry Raze add shades of techno in his remix. Rousing remix will work nice as a mix starter, Amarilyo also deliver deep and dark sound... Enjoy', NULL, NULL, 'INME &amp; 8.30AM - Bustling Space (Original Mix)<br />\r\nINME &amp; 8.30AM - Bustling Space (Amarilyo Remix)<br />\r\nINME &amp; 8.30AM - Bustling Space (Rousing Remix)<br />\r\nINME &amp; 8.30AM - Bustling Space (Terry Raze Remix)', 1, '2016-05-16 15:54:02', '2016-05-16 15:54:02'),
