(1706, 303, '4ykLive - One Man Band (the Album)', 'CTS303153', '2015-09-04', '1706_s.jpg', 'https://pro.beatport.com/release/one-man-band-the-album/1599705', 'https://pro.beatport.com/release/one-man-band-the-album/1599705', 'Every Summer CTS release some unusual vibes, for 2015 Summer and Autumn connection we choose instrumental Hip Hop and Downtempo album by newcomer 4ykLive. The sounds immediately drop into dark city paths adventure. Viscous leads and liquid atmospheres are winding between skyscrapers of rhythm patterns and wide pad squares, under the noise rays of night streetlights. Moreover the album is impregnated with Ukrainian melodic melancholy and accessorized with variety sound details that makes it complete...', NULL, NULL, '4ykLive - A Little Too Late<br />\r\n4ykLive - Cossack&lsquo;s Fate<br />\r\n4ykLive - One Man Band<br />\r\n4ykLive - It s About Soul<br />\r\n4ykLive - Crow<br />\r\n4ykLive - Ayawaska<br />\r\n4ykLive - Lost In The Ocean<br />\r\n4ykLive - 23.59<br />\r\n4ykLive - Muse<br />\r\n4ykLive - Out Of Space', 1, '2016-05-16 15:49:34', '2016-05-16 15:49:34'),
