(1710, 305, 'Dasero - Off The Ground EP', 'CTS305153', '2015-09-25', '1710_s.jpg', 'https://pro.beatport.com/release/off-the-ground-ep/1611867', 'https://pro.beatport.com/release/off-the-ground-ep/1611867', 'New EP by Dasero on CTS is deep and dark. Two brand new hypnotic after party bangers are made in underground tech house esthetics. Rich rhythmic texture and atonal synth elements allow the perception of non-linear plot of the works... off the ground..', NULL, NULL, 'Dasero - Off The Ground<br />\r\nDasero - The Best Is Yet To Come', 1, '2016-05-16 15:43:19', '2016-05-16 15:43:19'),
(1712, 306, 'Yuriy Berliny - Little Story EP', 'CTS306153', '2015-10-02', '1712_s.jpg', 'https://pro.beatport.com/release/little-story-ep/1616689', 'https://pro.beatport.com/release/little-story-ep/1616689', 'Another EP by Yuriy Berliny on CTS is deep tech-house and minimal. Three brand new tracks are complement each other creating a complete picture of a mini album...', '', NULL, 'Yuriy Berliny - Crazy Monday<br />\r\nYuriy Berliny - Little Story<br />\r\nYuriy Berliny - Selesta', 1, '2016-11-22 13:36:28', '2016-11-22 13:36:28'),
(1714, 307, 'Vitalii Sky - Sunny Day EP', 'CTS307153', '2015-10-16', '1714_s.jpg', 'https://pro.beatport.com/release/sunny-day-ep/1628838', 'https://pro.beatport.com/release/sunny-day-ep/1628838', 'Native Ukrainian instrument parts in combination with tech-house and deep house sounds made by Vitalii Sky forms organic conjunction. Thus the Sunny Day mini-album was born. Melancholic melodic ethno motives intertwined with rhythm patterns and groovy vibrations create an atmosphere of boundless steppe and clad peaks. It is a primordial feeling of the wind noise and air transparency around.', NULL, NULL, 'Vitalii SkY - Children Wide Fields<br />\r\nVitalii SkY - On the Waves of the Dnipro<br />\r\nVitalii SkY - Remember What You Forgot<br />\r\nVitalii SkY - Sunny Day<br />\r\nVitalii SkY - Ukrainian Cossack Rhythms', 1, '2016-05-16 15:33:54', '2016-05-16 15:33:54'),
(1716, 308, 'Massimo Gentile - Souspance', 'CTS308153', '2015-11-27', '1716_s.jpg', 'https://pro.beatport.com/release/souspance/1659709', 'https://pro.beatport.com/release/souspance/1659709', 'Brand new tech-house tune by Massimo Gentile on CTS will fulfill all expectations. Made mostly in techno esthetics have punchy tech-house shades as well. Pushy groove is supplemented with deep and noisy synth elements and &nbsp;ragged voices... bang your crowd!', '', NULL, 'Massimo Gentile - Souspance', 1, '2016-08-04 11:07:51', '2016-08-04 11:07:51'),
