(1798, 322, 'THE BEST PROGRESSIVE IN UA (VOL.6)', 'CTS322163', '2016-08-12', '1798_s.jpg', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/the-best-progressive-in-ua-vol-6/1828389', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/the-best-progressive-in-ua-vol-6/1828389', 'CTS Records presents the best Progressive tracks of the year by Ukrainian producers.', 'CTS Records представляет лучшие треки года в жанре Progressive от украинских исполнителей.', NULL, 'Andy Groove - Shamer&nbsp;<br />\r\nArt Alien - Three Of Us&nbsp;<br />\r\nCherry &amp; Andi Vax - Miracle&nbsp;<br />\r\nDaniel X - Your Way&nbsp;<br />\r\ndENNY SunShine - Tomor&nbsp;<br />\r\nEdward Madison - The City of Dreams (Edit Mix)<br />\r\nGeorge Gee - Space Breeze&nbsp;<br />\r\nIgor Graphite - Closer&nbsp;<br />\r\nMario - I Feel Paradise&nbsp;<br />\r\nMax Sajnev - Past&nbsp;<br />\r\nNeopoly Project - Innervision&nbsp;<br />\r\nNeopoly Project - Pandora&nbsp;<br />\r\nONE Spirit - King&nbsp;<br />\r\nPafosnyh - Instants&nbsp;<br />\r\nSoundlife - I Wish You Stay&nbsp;', 1, '2016-08-26 15:29:30', '2016-08-26 15:29:30'),
(1800, 323, 'struCTS vol.15', 'CTS323163', '2016-08-23', '1800_s.jpg', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/structs-vol-15/1833572', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/structs-vol-15/1833572', 'Fifteenth struCTS compilation is about Techno, House and Electronica. As usually only most wanted tracks are included...', 'Пятнадцатая сборка struCTS с Techno, House и Electronica. Как всегда,&nbsp;включены только наилучшие треки...', NULL, 'Esford - Black Room<br />\r\nBrain Control - I&#39;m at Home<br />\r\nDe&#39;mystique - BassFriction<br />\r\nMiguel Rodriguez - Rollerblast<br />\r\nAlexandr Zarva - September<br />\r\nRousing - There Where Are You<br />\r\nHaxxy - Sole Voce<br />\r\nDaniel X - Sonar<br />\r\nSK85 - Blind<br />\r\nNeopoly Project - Piano Waves<br />\r\nSeth&amp;Rise - Modestina<br />\r\nDropboy - Mojahet<br />\r\nMoon Shot &amp; CJ EDU - Haze<br />\r\nSeth&amp;Rise - Listen The End', 1, '2016-09-20 12:57:12', '2016-09-20 12:57:12'),
(1802, 324, 'CTSpaces EP vol.6', 'CTS234163', '2016-09-23', '1802_s.jpg', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/ctspaces-ep-vol-6/1854951', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/ctspaces-ep-vol-6/1854951', 'Next CTSpaces EP shows different shades of techno sound. From melodic and bass focused tune by DJ KoT and minimal groove by Dmitrty Dorohan to tight dynamic work by Roman Sweet... feel the vibe..', 'Следующий CTSpaces EP показывает различные оттенки techno. От мелодичной и басовитой мелодии от DJ KoT и minimal groove от&nbsp;Dmitrty Dorohan к жесткой динамичной работе Roman Sweet... почувствуй атмосферу..', NULL, 'Dmitrty Dorohan - Ocean<br />\r\nRoman Sweet - Planet Mus<br />\r\nDJ KoT - Stellarium', 1, '2016-09-23 13:12:53', '2016-09-23 13:12:53'),
(1803, 325, 'CTSpaces EP vol.7', 'CTS325163', '2016-10-14', '1803_s.jpg', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/ctspaces-ep-vol-7/1869498', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/ctspaces-ep-vol-7/1869498', 'For the seventh CTSpaces EP CTS prepared tech-house and deep house selection. As usual three brand new tracks which are shows different approaches, for this time, to techno and house genres crossing. All productions are colored with deep elements, make your choice!..', 'Для седьмого&nbsp;CTSpaces EP CTS приготовил отборный&nbsp;tech-house и deep house. Как обычно, 3 новых трека, которые показывают разные подходы, для этого времени, пересечение&nbsp;techno и house. Все треки украшены елементами&nbsp;deep&#39;а, сделай свой выбор..', NULL, 'Anish Anand - Bow Wow<br />\r\nMacroVision - Skyroom<br />\r\nMarVer - Balance', 1, '2016-10-21 11:02:33', '2016-10-21 11:02:33');
