(1811, 330, 'CTSmashers Part 9', 'CTS330173', '2017-01-30', '1811_s.jpg', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/ctsmashers-part-9/1939786', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/ctsmashers-part-9/1939786', 'For 9th CTSmashers compilation, CTS selected dozen of House tunes, Deep and Tech-House directed collection includes also hot Garage tracks... Enjoy...', 'Для 9й подборки&nbsp;CTSmashers, CTS выбрал дюжину&nbsp;House, Deep и Tech-House направленную коллекцию с гарячими&nbsp;Garage треками... Наслаждайтесь...', NULL, 'Boom Chilla - October<br />\r\nAlexandr Zarva - September<br />\r\nRousing - There Where Are You<br />\r\nNEOPOLY Project - Piano Waves<br />\r\nMonovakzin - Over<br />\r\nMassimo Gentile - Moody<br />\r\nINME &amp; 8.30AM - Bustling Space (Terry Raze Remix)<br />\r\nTerry Raze - Intek<br />\r\nDaniel X &nbsp;- Kyiv House<br />\r\nMarc Franco - Yokito<br />\r\nEsford - Black Room<br />\r\nNeural Clan - Stop Rollin Your Bones (&amp;listen2me)', 1, '2017-01-30 16:11:32', '2017-01-30 16:11:32'),
(1812, 331, 'CTSmashers Part 10', 'CTS331173', '2017-02-01', '1812_s.jpg', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/ctsmashers-part-10/1942620', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/ctsmashers-part-10/1942620', 'CTSmashers Part 10 is dedicated to Techno. Twelve selected tunes with shades of Tech-House, Deep, Melodic Techno and main room sound as well... Enjoy...&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTracks on this compilation are supported and reviewed by:&nbsp;Seb Fontaine&nbsp;<em>(Global Underground, Virgin, Thrive, United Kingdom)</em>, DJ Fresh <em>(Brooklyn DJ Factory, Niketalk Magazine, United States)</em>,&nbsp;Jayson Holden <em>(Non-Descript Records, Australia)</em>, DJMGee <em>(Alando Palais, Germany)</em>,&nbsp;DJ DiRRty HaRRi&nbsp;<em>(Derek Harri / Sonic Music Prod, 2 Tone Music / Tony &amp; Adam&#39;s, Thunder Bay, Canada)</em>, Soundfausto&nbsp;<em>(Argentina)</em>, Dj-fifi&nbsp;<em>(Belgium)</em>,&nbsp;PK Live <em>(Zeitgeist (Curitiba)</em>, <em>Garage Club, Festival Synergy, Brazil)</em>,&nbsp;Joe C&nbsp;<em>(Mixmag, Ground Level Records, United States)</em>,&nbsp;DJ Richard Lewis&nbsp;<em>(Metro-Stereo,United Kingdom)</em>, DJ Navarro&nbsp;<em>(LAD Publishing &amp; Records, New Zealand)</em>, and many more...\r\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong><a href=\"http://cts-label.com/reviews/\">r</a></strong><a href=\"http://cts-label.com/reviews/\"><strong>ead reviews</strong></a></div>\r\n', 'CTSmashers Part 10 посвящен&nbsp;Techno. Двенадцать отборных треков с оттенками&nbsp;Tech-House, Deep и Melodic Techno... Наслаждайтесь...<br />\r\n<br />\r\nТреки из этой компиляции поддержали:&nbsp;Seb Fontaine&nbsp;<em>(Global Underground, Virgin, Thrive, United Kingdom)</em>, DJ Fresh <em>(Brooklyn DJ Factory, Niketalk Magazine, United States)</em>,&nbsp;Jayson Holden <em>(Non-Descript Records, Australia)</em>, DJMGee <em>(Alando Palais, Germany)</em>,&nbsp;DJ DiRRty HaRRi&nbsp;<em>(Derek Harri / Sonic Music Prod, 2 Tone Music / Tony &amp; Adam&#39;s, Thunder Bay, Canada)</em>, Soundfausto&nbsp;<em>(Argentina)</em>, Dj-fifi&nbsp;<em>(Belgium)</em>,&nbsp;PK Live <em>(Zeitgeist (Curitiba)</em>, <em>Garage Club, Festival Synergy, Brazil)</em>,&nbsp;Joe C&nbsp;<em>(Mixmag, Ground Level Records, United States)</em>,&nbsp;DJ Richard Lewis&nbsp;<em>(Metro-Stereo,United Kingdom)</em>, DJ Navarro&nbsp;<em>(LAD Publishing &amp; Records, New Zealand)</em>, and many more... и многие другие...\r\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><a href=\"http://cts-label.com/reviews/\"><strong>читать ревью</strong></a></div>\r\n', NULL, 'Moon Shot &amp; CJ EDU - HAZE<br />\r\nSeth&amp;Rise - Listen The End<br />\r\nMechanical Wave - Exp<br />\r\nYuriy Berliny - Selesta<br />\r\nAVC - Gate Gate<br />\r\nDe`mystique - BassFriction<br />\r\nLime K - 24th Floor<br />\r\nBrain Control - I&#39;m At Home<br />\r\nMiguel Rodriguez - Rollerblast<br />\r\nDaniel X - Code Red<br />\r\nDaniel X - Sonar<br />\r\nSeth&amp;Rise - Therapy', 1, '2017-02-14 14:13:48', '2017-02-14 14:13:48'),
(1813, 332, 'Mark Faderfaz - Master Beat EP', 'CTS332173', '2017-02-17', '1813_s.jpg', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/mark-faderfaz-master-beat-ep/1954330', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EpmbmiHPYWo&index=34&t=0s&list=PLGgnjVlZCVJl01-ETqdd4R8HSyfZwlfqp', 'Mark Faderfaz deliver a new solid portion of underground house sound with his Master Beat EP on CTS. Hot pumping grooves are supplemented with deep and old school elements, all the mixture is spiced with low vocal parts and expressive shouts...<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPrevious EP of Mark Faderfaz is supported by well known artists like <em>Gene Farris</em> <em>(Defected, Cajual, SOMA, Farris Wheel, United States)</em>, Kenny Summit&nbsp;(<em>Defected, Good For You Records,</em>&nbsp;<em>United States</em>), DJ Fresh (<em>Brooklyn DJ Factory, Niketalk Magazine, United States</em>) and also by Haldo (<em>Proceed Records, Italy</em>), DJ John Christy (<em>JC Enterprises, Ministry of Sound, United Kingdom</em>), Gianmarco Oglietti (<em>GROSSO!, Bears Invasion, LO Aperitivo, Italy</em>), Larry Tee&nbsp;(<em>LOVE MACHINE MUSIC INC., DANR RECORDS, United States</em>), Mike Egloff (<em>Various venues (clubs and lounges) Switzerland</em>)&nbsp;and many more..<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://cts-label.com/reviews/?page=2\">read reviews</a>', 'В своем Master Beat EP, Mark Faderfaz представил новую солидную порцию андеграундного house саунда на&nbsp;CTS Records. Горячий качевый грув&nbsp;дополнен элементами deep и old school, все треки ЕР приправлены различными вокальнми семплами от low vocal parts до експрессивных shouts...<br />\r\n<br />\r\nПредыдущий ЕР Mark Faderfaz поддержали известные артисты, среди которых&nbsp;<em>Gene Farris</em> <em>(Defected, Cajual, SOMA, Farris Wheel, United States)</em>, Kenny Summit&nbsp;(<em>Defected, Good For You Records,</em>&nbsp;<em>United States</em>), DJ Fresh (<em>Brooklyn DJ Factory, Niketalk Magazine, United States</em>), а также Haldo (<em>Proceed Records, Italy</em>), DJ John Christy (<e