(1816, 334, 'Yan Oxygen - Running Kiev EP', 'CTS334173', '2017-04-14', '1816_s.jpg', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/running-kiev-ep/1999148', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ep2C5s3p2BI&index=23&t=0s&list=PLGgnjVlZCVJl01-ETqdd4R8HSyfZwlfqp', 'Well known techno artist Yan Oxygen deliver melodic and dark underground grooves with his&nbsp;brand new release on CTS. Both of two tracks are atmospheric, full of deepness and supplemented&nbsp;with voicelike FXs. Tight Labyrinth&#39;s soundscape disclosed in a strong drop. Running Kiev is&nbsp;spiced with voice adds, more focused on drum parts but also made in the main aesthetics of a&nbsp;sign sound of Yan Oxygen... feel the vibe! &nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSupported by:&nbsp;<br />\r\nAnna V. (Addeepted, Three Squares, Greece), Diction(Society Music, LW Recordings , Netherlands),&nbsp;&nbsp;DJ Lakey (ADSR Records, United States), M.I.D.I. (Akoom Records, Dolma Records, Italy),&nbsp;Henrique Mancha (D.edge, Brasil),&nbsp;Maydan (Asymmetric Recordings, Incorrect Records, Israel),&nbsp;DJ Fresh (Brooklyn DJ Factory, Scene, Niketalk Magazine, USA),&nbsp;Linda Leigh (Technotica, Burst Radio Detroit and EJR Radio Amsterdam, United States),&nbsp;Nick Nemisz (Habitat Living Sound, Canada),&nbsp;Anton Tseslik (Kiss FM, Ukraine),&nbsp;Willem Paul (Control Room, Techno Tuesday, Netherlands),&nbsp;Gaty Lopez (No-Logik, KULT (New York), Pacha Recordings, Ibiza),&nbsp;Lucas Freire (Different Is Different Records, Nothing But, Brasil) and many more...<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://cts-label.com/reviews/\">Read reviews</a>', 'Известный техно артист Yan Oxygen, со своим новым ЕР релизом на CTS, доставил свежий мелодичный и дарковый андерграундный грув прямо из своей студии. Атмосферные и насыщенные дип элементами, оба трека дополнены вокальными еффектами. Soundscape плотного Labyrinth расскрывается в ярком дропе. В свою очередь, Running Kiev, приправленный вокальными деталями, больше сфокусирован на барабанных партиях, но в то же время, выполнен в фирменной эстетике саунда от Yan Oxygen... feel the vibe! \r\n\r\nSupported by: \r\nAnna V. (Addeepted, Three Squares, Greece), Diction(Society Music, LW Recordings , Netherlands),  DJ Lakey (ADSR Records, United States), M.I.D.I. (Akoom Records, Dolma Records, Italy), Henrique Mancha (D.edge, Brasil), Maydan (Asymmetric Recordings, Incorrect Records, Israel), DJ Fresh (Brooklyn DJ Factory, Scene, Niketalk Magazine, USA), Linda Leigh (Technotica, Burst Radio Detroit and EJR Radio Amsterdam, United States), Nick Nemisz (Habitat Living Sound, Canada), Anton Tseslik (Kiss FM, Ukraine), Willem Paul (Control Room, Techno Tuesday, Netherlands), Gaty Lopez (No-Logik, KULT (New York), Pacha Recordings, Ibiza), Lucas Freire (Different Is Different Records, Nothing But, Brasil) and many more...<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://cts-label.com/reviews/\">Read reviews</a>', NULL, '<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ep2C5s3p2BI&amp;list=PLGgnjVlZCVJl01-ETqdd4R8HSyfZwlfqp&amp;index=23\">Yan Oxygen -&nbsp;Labyrinth</a><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qdH6BdTNkD0&amp;index=24&amp;list=PLGgnjVlZCVJl01-ETqdd4R8HSyfZwlfqp\">Yan Oxygen - Running Kiev</a>', 1, '2019-10-05 14:23:45', '2019-10-05 14:23:45'),
(1817, 335, 'Technolog - Mutto EP', 'CTS335173', '2017-06-09', '1817_s.jpg', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/mutto-ep/2041146', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Uh4VolHXQHc&index=22&t=3s&list=PLGgnjVlZCVJl01-ETqdd4R8HSyfZwlfqp', 'Technolog in his best sound! For Mutto EP this underground artist deliver techno sound with well thought out deep touch. Devon is most soft and atmospheric part of the selection with almost house feel, Mutto as a head track of the album is tight and dark, Calm is made is slow rhythm aestetics amd have original impressive melodic hook, faster and stronger Extract is influenced with acid techno traditions and logicaly finalize the EP.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSupported by:<br />\r\nNick Fiorucci (zipDJ, Canada), Gino Lightner (CODE 21, Netherlands), Matt Moore (Matt&#39;s Bar, Portugal), DJ Fresh (Brooklyn DJ Factory, USA), Kelee Haggarty (Hollywood Dance Radio, Canada), Don Nalin (Radio Webphre, Sri Lanka), Matthew Wasley (Human Life, USA), Luca Cucchetti (RadioDanceMusic, Italy), Bryant Littlejohn (Global Vibes MixShow, USA), Maurizio Santi (Promotionalrecord, Italy) and many more...<a href=\"http://cts-label.com/reviews/\">Read reviews</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;', 'Technolog в своем лучшем techno амплуа! Для Mutto EP этот андеграундный артист подготовил techno саунд с хорошо продуманным дип сочетанием. Devon - наиболее мягкая и атмосферная составляющая сборника с почти house ощущением; звук Mutto, главного трека альбома, плотный и темный; Calm с впечатляющим, оригинальным мелодическим хуком, сделан в slow rhythm эстетике; выполненный в acid techno традициях Extract, жестче и быстрее остальных номеров, логически завершает EP.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSupported by:<br />\r\nNick Fiorucci (zipDJ, Canada), Gino Lightner (CODE 21, Netherlands), Matt Moore (Matt&#39;s Bar, Portugal), DJ Fresh (Brooklyn DJ Factory, USA), Kelee Haggarty (Hollywood Dance Radio, Canada), Don Nalin (Radio Webphre, Sri Lanka), Matthew Wasley (Human Life, USA), Luca Cucchetti (RadioDanceMusic, Italy), Bryant Littlejohn (Global Vibes MixShow, USA), Maurizio Santi (Promotionalrecord, Italy) and many more...<a href=\"http://cts-label.com/reviews/\">Read reviews</a>', NULL, '<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Uh4VolHXQHc&amp;list=PLGgnjVlZCVJl01-ETqdd4R8HSyfZwlfqp&amp;index=22\">Technolog - Mutto</a><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UtikUvLwv2E&amp;list=PLGgnjVlZCVJl01-ETqdd4R8HSyfZwlfqp&amp;index=20\">Technolog - Extract</a><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3o9KFGYMXOQ&amp;list=PLGgnjVlZCVJl01-ETqdd4R8HSyfZwlfqp&amp;index=21\">Technolog - Calm</a><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2FjyAw6e6ik&amp;list=PLGgnjVlZCVJl01-ETqdd4R8HSyfZwlfqp&amp;index=19\">Technolog - Devon</a>', 1, '2018-02-23 16:04:35', '2018-02-23 16:04:35'),
(1818, 336, 'Filya Trevelyan - Monotraks EP', 'CTS336173', '2017-09-08', '1818_s.jpg', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/monotraks-ep/2104470', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=24HB5Hwf5yQ&index=18&t=0s&list=PLGgnjVlZCVJl01-ETqdd4R8HSyfZwlfqp', 'We are happy to welcome Finnish DJ &amp; producer Filya Trevelyan with his debut EP on CTS. 3 brand new techno tracks all shows different sides of techno. All tracks are trippy with a gradually unfolding plot, &quot;Autumn&quot; is dark and dirty,&nbsp;atmospheric &quot;404&quot; and another one is faster - &quot;Chicago&quot; with strong and tight groove.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSupported by:<br />\r\nPK Live (Garage Club, Festival Synergy, Brazil),&nbsp;DJ Fresh (Brooklyn DJ Factory, Scene, Niketalk Magazine, USA),&nbsp;Maurizio Santi (Promotionalrecord, Modena Radio City, Radio Mela, Gonnosfanadiga, Italy),&nbsp;Markus Baumhackl (NiteFlight, Austria),&nbsp;DJ Trouble (Foo bar, Italy),&nbsp;DJ DiRRty HaRRi (Sonic Music Prod, 2 Tone Music, Tony &amp; Adam&#39;s, Thunder Bay, Canada), &nbsp;DJ Lothar (Der Gardinen-Service, Shagall, Germany),&nbsp;RIshi Bass (Sound of Music, Netherlands), DJ Lakey (ADSR Records, USA),&nbsp;Jayson Butera (Elliptical Sun, VIM Recordings, USA), Bryant LittleJhon (Global Vibes Mixshow, USA),&nbsp;Linda Leigh (Technotica, Burst Radio Detroit and EJR Radio Amsterdam, USA) and many more...<a href=\"http://cts-label.com/reviews/\">Read reviews</a>', 'Мы рады представить ди-джея и продюсера Filya Trevelyan из Финляндии, с его дебютным EP на CTS. В составе релиза 3 новых techno трека, которые показывают разные грани techno музыки. Всем работам характерно плавное развитие сюжетных линий. Саунд &quot;Autumn&quot; грязный и темный, &quot;404&quot; построен на атмосферах, темп &quot;Chicago&quot;, значительно более быстрый с жестким и плотным грувом.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSupported by:<br />\r\nPK Live (Garage Club, Festival Synergy, Brazil),&nbsp;DJ Fresh (Brooklyn DJ Factory, Scene, Niketalk Magazine, USA)