(1831, 346, 'Monovakzin - Zombie Robot\'s Moving', 'CTS 346183', '2018-04-20', '1831_s.jpg', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/zombie-robots-moving-ep/2271700', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r9Ez4HIgrG0&index=1&list=PLGgnjVlZCVJl01-ETqdd4R8HSyfZwlfqp&t=5s', 'On &quot;Zombie Robot&#39;s Moving&quot; EP Monovakzin deliver disco influenced sound with analog synth and vocoder parts. In three brand new tracks vintage disco touch is supplemented with modern and tight deep house groove.&nbsp;', '', NULL, '<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r9Ez4HIgrG0&amp;index=1&amp;list=PLGgnjVlZCVJl01-ETqdd4R8HSyfZwlfqp&amp;t=5s\">Monovakzin - Feel ill</a><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/IFrAvToNfgs\">Monovakzin - TIME2</a><br />\r\nMonovakzin - Zombie Robot&#39;s Moving', 1, '2018-05-16 09:41:25', '2018-05-16 09:41:25');
