(1832, 347, 'struCTS vol.17', 'CTS 347183', '2018-05-04', '1832_s.jpg', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/structs-vol-17/2281143', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/structs-vol-17/2281143', 'Seventeenth struCTS is about House, Techno and Tech-House, as always only the best stuff. For this compilation we picked out our favorite tunes ready for dancefloor.<br />\r\n<strong>Supported by:</strong>&nbsp;<br />\r\nGene Farris (Defected Records, SOMA, United States),&nbsp;Nick Fiorucci (zipDJ, Hi-Bias, zipCAST.fm, Canada),&nbsp;Ingo Vogelmann (friskyRadio, German), Ben Salem (Innervisions radio, United States), DJ Bryant (Global Vibes MixShow, United States),&nbsp;DJ Lakey (ADSR Records, United States),&nbsp;Manny Ward (Many Words Music, United States),&nbsp;Stella Elmendorp (Cindystar6, Ashtendorp, United Kingdom),&nbsp;DJ Blackprint (London Pirate Radio, England),&nbsp;DJ Mondo (MixCloud/Beatport,&nbsp;United States),&nbsp;Torsten Jodat (Freies Radio Goeppingen - Radio fips, Germany),&nbsp;Jay (France),&nbsp;Linda Leigh (Technotica, Burst Radio Detroit and EJR Radio Amsterdam, United States),&nbsp;DJ Monta (Reserved Records, Italy),&nbsp;Stefano Vaglio (T Club, Italy),&nbsp;Jean-Pierre Chacon (WVMLO, USA),&nbsp;Arron Saunders (SaunderZ , DistinctFm , Bromsgrove, United Kingdom),&nbsp;PK Live (Zeitgeist (Curitiba), Garage Club, Festival Synergy, Brazil),&nbsp;Doppelagenten (Tanzbar Palette, Germany),&nbsp;Susana Egea (Spain),&nbsp;Gianmarco Oglietti (Caffe del Progresso, Italy),&nbsp;Warren Star (FlipFlops Beach Club, Qatar),&nbsp;TJ Pak (GuessWhat, Conquer Entertainment, Cassette Nine, New Zealand),&nbsp;Jacob Reyes (Sleepy Genius, LEVEL, United States)&nbsp;and many more... <a href=\"http://cts-label.com/reviews/\">Read Reviews</a>&nbsp;', 'Семнадцатый выпуск struCTS посвящен House, Techno и Tech-House, как всегда, только лучший материал. Для этой компиляции мы отобрали наши любимые треки специально для танцпола.&nbsp;', NULL, 'Binary Energy - Tale Of The Night<br />\r\nAdellacosta - Hollow&nbsp;Original Mix<br />\r\nRoman Sweet - Mrs. Cat<br />\r\nVitalii Sky - Magic House<br />\r\nPruha - Icarus<br />\r\nSergio Mega - Stereoland (Carl Bee Remix)<br />\r\nSqalektiq - Paradox<br />\r\nJorhero - Last Dawn&nbsp;<br />\r\nVitamindevil - Lemon Juice<br />\r\nYan Oxygen - Tray', 1, '2018-05-16 09:41:25', '2018-05-16 09:41:25'),
(1833, 348, 'Sergio Mega - City Breathing EP', 'CTS 348183', '2018-05-29', '1833_s.jpg', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/city-breathing/2301334', 'https://youtu.be/3YtR-XcRFUI', 'With &ldquo;City Breathing&rdquo; EP we start releasing brand new album of Sergio Mega &ldquo;Back 2 The Future&rdquo;. Ambient preamble &ldquo;Alone On The Clouds&rdquo; conveys a feeling of calm andserenity as well as a loneliness sensation in a boundless expanse. &ldquo;City Breathing&rdquo; is a unique combination of techno, disco, acid and ambient. The track video is stylized as a short documentary and has a social orientation. It is focused on a city soul searching, urbanization of life and also on reasoning over a certain revaluation of values, that so far the existence of a modern human being requires. Enjoy the first part of this multimedia puzzle!', 'С &laquo;City Breathing&raquo; EP мы начинаем выпуск нового альбома Sergio Mega &laquo;Back 2 The Future&raquo;. Ambient преамбула &laquo;Alone On The Clouds&raquo; передает чувства спокойствия и безмятежности, а также ощущение одиночества в безграничных просторах. &laquo;City Breathing&raquo; - уникальное сочетание techno, disco, acid и ambient. Видео трека стилизовано под короткий документальный фильм и имеет социальную ориентацию. Концепция фокусирует внимание на поиске души города, урбанизации жизни, а также на рассуждении о некоторой переоценке ценностей, которой сегодня требует бытие современного человека. Наслаждайтесь первой частью этой мультимедийной головоломки!', NULL, '<a href=\"https://youtu.be/AGc4j5cs9GE\">Alone on The Clouds</a><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3YtR-XcRFUI\">City Breathing</a>', 1, '2018-05-29 18:42:20', '2018-05-29 18:42:20'),
(1834, 349, 'Onien - Back Up EP', 'CTS 349183', '2018-06-15', '1834_s.jpg', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/back-up-ep/2317851', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/back-up-ep/2317851', '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">We&#39;d like to welcome Onien with Back UP EP on CTS! Serbian techno artist deliver strong tight and in a same time melodic groove with two brand new tracks. At Her Majesty&#39;s Service is dark and melodic made with underground progressive influences. The title track Back Up is more focused on drums and bass parts it more pulsatile but still melodic as an artist&#39;s sign sound.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSupported by: Marco Carola (Music On, Italy), Steve &#39;Butch&#39; Jones (Something Global, UK), Suzy Solar (Neurodisc/Capitol Records, Magic Island Records, Universal Nation, Supercomps, USA),&nbsp;Three CP (DataTech, Lenjam Records, Big Mamas House, Switzerland),&nbsp;DJ Angola (Deckstatic, No 8, Space Ibiza NYC, USA),&nbsp;Matt Rowan (Baroque, Hope, Proton, Australia), Frisco (Yellow House, Spain),&nbsp;Robbie Jay (Plasticity Records, Romania),&nbsp;DJ Fresh (Brooklyn DJ Factory, Niketalk Magazine, USA),&nbsp;DJ Bhryant (Global Vibes MixShow, USA),&nbsp;Kris Von (Ausara Recordings, Bulgaria),&nbsp;Linda Leigh&nbsp;(Technotica, Burst Radio Detroit and EJR Radio Amsterdam, USA),&nbsp;Norbert Meszes (Karmaloft, Phunk Traxx, Hungary),&nbsp;Sergio Matina (Alchemist Of Sound, Tendenzia Records, Italy),&nbsp;HatStandy (Ghost Fat Productions, AlexMos, Morality Records, UK),&nbsp;Joseph Christopher (Dakota West Recordings, 4Beat Records, USA) and many more... <a href=\"http://cts-label.com/reviews/\">Read Reviews</a></div>\r\n', '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">We&#39;d like to welcome Onien with &quot;Back Up&quot; EP on CTS! Serbian techno artist deliver strong tight and in a same time melodic groove with two brand new tracks. &quot;At Her Majesty&#39;s Service&quot; is dark and melodic made with underground progressive influences. The title track &quot;Back Up&quot; is more focused on drums and bass parts it more pulsatile but still melodic as an artist&#39;s sign sound.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSupported by: Marco Carola (Music On, Italy), Steve &#39;Butch&#39; Jones (Something Global, UK), Suzy Solar (Neurodisc/Capitol Records, Magic Island Records, Universal Nation, Supercomps, USA),&nbsp;Three CP (DataTech, Lenjam Records, Big Mamas House, Switzerland),&nbsp;DJ Angola (Deckstatic, No 8, Space Ibiza NYC, USA),&nbsp;Matt Rowan (Baroque, Hope, Proton, Australia), Frisco (Yellow House, Spain),&nbsp;Robbie Jay (Plasticity Records, Romania),&nbsp;DJ Fresh (Brooklyn DJ Factory, Niketalk Magazine, USA),&nbsp;DJ Bhryant (Global Vibes MixShow, USA),&nbsp;Kris Von (Ausara Recordings, Bulgaria),&nbsp;Linda Leigh&nbsp;(Technotica, Burst Radio Detroit and EJR Radio Amsterdam, USA),&nbsp;Norbert Meszes (Karmaloft, Phunk Traxx, Hungary),&nbsp;Sergio Matina (Alchemist Of Sound, Tendenzia Records, Italy),&nbsp;HatStandy (Ghost Fat Productions, AlexMos, Morality Records, UK),&nbsp;Joseph Christopher (Dakota West Recordings, 4Beat Records, USA) and many more... <a href=\"http://cts-label.com/reviews/\">Read Reviews</a></div>\r\n', NULL, '<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PPIcf1YhH-c\">Onien -&nbsp;At Her Majesty&#39;s Service</a><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-eMRdbRvmK0\">Onien -&nbsp;Back Up</a>', 1, '2018-07-30 17:01:31', '2018-07-30 17:01:31'),
(1836, 350, 'Vitalii Sky - Vinyl Memories', 'CTS 350183', '2018-07-17', '1836_s.jpg', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/vinyl-memories-ep/2340237', 'https://youtu.be/yjDQZt8bsEc', '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Groovy and pumping sound is coming out with new EP by Vitalii Sky. &quot;Vinyl Memories&quot; is made in deep techno aesthetics and have tight strong beat along with housy chords, vinyl noise and old school house influneced elements. &quot;White Nights&quot; is fitly complimented with timbres of Ukrainian native instrument trembita which adds originality to this UA house example... Enjoy!</div>\r\n', '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Снова грувистый, качающий саунд от&nbsp;Vitalii Sky в его новом ЕР на CTS. &quot;Vinyl Memories&quot; с плотным жестким ритмом соседствующим с дип аккордами и хрустом виниловой пластинки, в целом можно отнести к deep techno эстетике.&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;White Nights&quot; удачно дополнен тембрами украинских народных духовых инструментов - трембит, что добавляет оригинальности этому образцу&nbsp;UA house...&nbsp;Enjoy!</div>\r\n', NULL, '<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yjDQZt8bsEc\">Vitalii Sky - Vinyl Memories</a><br />\r\nVitalii Sky - White Nights', 1, '2018-07-27 10:48:08', '2018-07-27 10:48:08'),
(1837, 351, 'UUOO - Stay Down EP', 'CTS 351183', '2018-08-17', '1837_s.jpg', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/stay-down-ep/2361185', 'https://youtu.be/gNSxra09KV4', '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">It&#39;s our pleasure to announce&nbsp;Stay Down EP by Birmingham UK based artist UUOO.&nbsp;As a multi faceted improvising artist UUOO channels elements from his wide range of abilities in music into his unique approach to techno, taking the listener on a journey of improvised discovery that exists to celebrate the immediacy of creation and collective participation. Somewhere in between the sound of analog synthesisers, trumpet, abstract vocals and atmospheric noise, UUOO grounds his music with the kind of hard hitting groove that can&rsquo;t be ignored.&nbsp;In the time UUOO has been a part of the global music scene he has collaborated with artists and the public in a huge varitey of settings including: Oxbow C.W. Stoneking Gonimoblast;&nbsp;John Baggott (Massive Attack, Portishead, Robert Plant) &amp; Daisy Palmer (Paloma Faith, Goldfrapp).<br />\r\nThe author say:<strong> Stay Down</strong>&nbsp;&quot;<em>is about forced transition &amp; the effects of social human behaviour. I wrote this tune over the course of two, very chaotic years in my life and the convoluted message i&#39;m trying to get across is that people need to try harder with each other by being patient and understanding. It&#39;s also a message to myself...</em>&quot;&nbsp;<strong>Ja</strong> &quot;<em>is like being thrown in ice water at 7am. I wanted to write something that was super danceable but also structurally confusing to the listener. I enjoy music the most when it defies your expectations slightly.</em>&quot;</div>\r\n', '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">It&#39;s our pleasure to announce&nbsp;Stay Down EP by Birmingham UK based artist UUOO.&nbsp;As a multi faceted improvising artist UUOO channels elements from his wide range of abilities in music into his unique approach to techno, taking the listener on a journey of improvised discovery that exists to celebrate the immediacy of creation and collective participation. Somewhere in between the sound of analog synthesisers, trumpet, abstract vocals and atmospheric noise, UUOO grounds his music with the kind of hard hitting groove that can&rsquo;t be ignored.&nbsp;In the time UUOO has been a part of the global music scene he has collaborated with artists and the public in a huge varitey of settings including: Oxbow C.W. Stoneking Gonimoblast;&nbsp;John Baggott (Massive Attack, Portishead, Robert Plant) &amp; Daisy Palmer (Paloma Faith, Goldfrapp).</div>\r\nThe author say:<strong> Stay Down</strong>&nbsp;&quot;<em>is about forced transition &amp; the effects of social human behaviour. I wrote this tune over the course of two, very chaotic years in my life and the convoluted message i&#39;m trying to get across is that people need to try harder with each other by being patient and understanding. It&#39;s also a message to myself...</em>&quot;&nbsp;<strong>Ja</strong> &quot;<em>is like being thrown in ice water at 7am. I wanted to write something that was super danceable but also structurally confusing to the listener. I enjoy music the most when it defies your expectations slightly.</em>&quot;', NULL, '<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gNSxra09KV4\" target=\"_blank\">UUOO - Stay Down</a><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/u8C7HRuRps4\" target=\"_blank\">UUOO - Ja</a>', 1, '2019-02-22 10:00:48', '2019-02-22 10:00:48'),
(1839, 352, 'interaCTS vol.1', 'CTS 352183', '2018-09-26', '1839_s.jpg', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/interacts-vol-1/2393382', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/interacts-vol-1/2393382', '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">We are glad to announce &quot;InteraCTS&quot; - new EP series! The concept is based on a finding common ground of two different artists sounds for each edition. For the &quot;volume one&quot; were selected two techy tracks. Monotonic techno tune &quot;Cybercube&quot; by Pruha and groovy tech-house production &quot;The Train Will Not Stop&quot; - debut of Solo Mind on CTS... Feel the vibe!</div>\r\n', '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">We are glad to announce &quot;InteraCTS&quot; - new EP series! The concept is based on a finding common ground of two different artists sounds for each edition. For the &quot;volume one&quot; were selected two techy tracks. Monotonic techno tune &quot;Cybercube&quot; by Pruha and groovy tech-house production &quot;The Train Will Not Stop&quot; - debut of Solo Mind on CTS... Feel the vibe!</div>\r\n', NULL, 'Renko - The Train Will Not Stop<br />\r\nPruha - Cybercube', 1, '2018-10-10 13:15:10', '2018-10-10 13:15:10'),
(1840, 353, 'R-Mix - Reflection', 'CTS 353183', '2018-11-02', '1840_s.jpg', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/reflection/2427021', '', 'We are welcome Iranian artist R-Mix on CTS with his new melodic techno tune Reflection. The track is made on the verge of techno and progressive with deep elements. Straight draw bassline is suplemented with sharper stabs and attack basses, along with deep melodic pads, dreamy arp and synth parts which are make their work for the track fullness and integrity as well.', 'We are welcome Iranian artist R-Mix on CTS with his new melodic techno tune Reflection. The track is made on the verge of techno and progressive with deep elements. Straight draw bassline is suplemented with sharper stabs and attack basses, along with deep melodic pads, dreamy arp and synth parts which are make their work for the track fullness and integrity as well.', NULL, 'R-Mix - Reflection', 1, '2019-02-27 18:06:16', '2019-02-27 18:06:16'),
(1842, 354, 'David Mayboroda - Again', 'CTS 354183', '2018-12-14', '1842_s.jpg', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/again/2463778', '', '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">David Mayboroda deliver atmospheric &amp; deep house sound with his debut &quot;Again&quot; EP on CTS. Original is very mild, soft and deep. Extended opens one more turn in the break. Wonderfull addition for the release is sunny and groovy remix by Deepstereo! Feel the vibe...</div>\r\n', '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">David Mayboroda deliver atmospheric &amp; deep house sound with his debut &quot;Again&quot; EP on CTS. Original is very mild, soft and deep. Extended opens one more turn in the break. Wonderfull addition for the release is sunny and groovy remix by Deepstereo! Feel the vibe...</div>\r\n', NULL, 'David Mayboroda - Again (Original Mix)<br />\r\nDavid Mayboroda - Again (Extended Mix)<br />\r\nDavid Mayboroda - Again (Deepstereo Remix)', 1, '2019-02-27 18:06:38', '2019-02-27 18:06:38'),
(1843, 355, 'Gaty Lopez - Show Me', 'CTS 355183', '2018-12-21', '1843_s.jpg', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/show-me/2468452', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/show-me/2468452', '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">We are welcome Gaty Lopez on CTS with his new house tune &quot;Show Me&quot;. Monotonic house original is supplemented with deep and disco influenced Monovakzin remix. Dark and strong basement sound and acid bassline of Sergio Mega remix opens another side of the release... Feel the vibe!&nbsp;</div>\r\n', '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">We are welcome Gaty Lopez on CTS with his new house tune &quot;Show Me&quot;. Monotonic house original is supplemented with deep and disco influenced Monovakzin remix. Dark and strong basement sound and acid bassline of Sergio Mega remix opens another side of the release... Feel the vibe!&nbsp;</div>\r\n', NULL, 'Gaty Lopez - Show Me (Original Mix)<br />\r\nGaty Lopez - Show Me (Monovakzin Remix)<br />\r\nGaty Lopez - Show Me (Sergio Mega Remix)', 1, '2019-03-04 10:10:16', '2019-03-04 10:10:16'),
(1844, 356, 'Ki Yera - Acid Pace', 'CTS 356193', '2019-04-05', '1844_s.jpg', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/acid-pace/2556960', 'https://youtu.be/e0-oeEBruvE', '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">We are wellcome Ukrainian new talent Ki Yera on CTS with her brand new track Acid Pace. Release is coming with Remixes influenced with different shades of underground house and techno sound based on original Ki Yera&#39;s acid bassline. Pruha, RAFO, Vitalii SkY and Monovakzin put their hands on this tune to complete the release.</div>\r\n', '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Мы рады приветствовать новый украинский талант&nbsp;Ki Yera на CTS с ее новым треком Acid Pace. В релиз вошли ремиксы, выполненные с влиянием&nbsp;различных оттенков андерграундного house и techno саунда. Все ремиксы&nbsp;базируются&nbsp;на оригинальной acid bass line Ki Yera. Ремиксы от Pruha, RAFO, Vitalii SkY и Monovakzin делают этот&nbsp;ЕР многогранным, завершаю релиз.</div>\r\n', '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ми вітаємо новий український талант Ki Yera на CTS з її новим треком Acid Pace. Реліз укомплектований&nbsp;реміксами, що виконані&nbsp;під впливом різних відтінків андерграундного house і techno-саунду&nbsp;на основі оригінальної acid bass line Кі Yera. Ремікси від Pruha, RAFO, Vitalii SkY і Monovakzin роблять цей ЕР багатогранним, завершуючи реліз.</div>\r\n', '<a href=\"https://youtu.be/e0-oeEBruvE\">Ki Yera - Acid Pace (Original Mix)</a><br />\r\nKi Yera - Acid Pace (Monovakzin Remix)<br />\r\nKi Yera - Acid Pace (Pruha Remix)<br />\r\nKi Yera - Acid Pace (RAFO Remix)<br />\r\nKi Yera - Acid Pace (Vitalii SkY Remix)', 1, '2019-04-22 14:15:38', '2019-04-22 14:15:38'),
(1846, 357, 'Monovakzin - Affinity Diagram', 'CTS 357193', '2019-05-17', '1846_s.jpg', '', '', '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Monovakzin deliverhis own view to modern disco sound with his Affinity Diagram EP. Vintage synth parts are supplemented with tight powerful groove which is made in a recognizable characteristic manner, but individually for each track. Hot Three!!!</div>\r\n', '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">В новом Affinity Diagram EP для CTS Monovakzin представил свой взгляд на современный диско саунд. Партии винтажных синтезаторов дополняются плотным мощным грувом, выполненном в узнаваемой характерной манере, но индивидуально для каждого трека. Горячая тройка !!!</div>\r\n', '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">У новому Affinity Diagram EP для CTS Monovakzin представив свій погляд на сучасний диско саунд. Партії вантажних синтезаторів доповнюються щільним потужним грувом, який виконано у впізнаваній характерній манері, але індивідуально для кожного треку. Гаряча трійка !!!</div>\r\n', 'Monovakzin - Affinity Diagram<br />\r\nMonovakzin - Arterial Road<br />\r\nMonovakzin - Pasteboard', 1, '2019-05-06 18:06:40', '2019-05-06 18:06:40'),
(1847, 358, 'Rayzers - Acid EP', 'CTS 358193', '2019-06-21', '1847_s.jpg', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/acid/2632082', '', '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Rayzers deliver two strong powerful techno tracks in his debut Acid EP on CTS. Ilex is dark and have expressive groove as well as perceptible house music connections in contradistinction to stright tight headline track of the EP which is dedicated to acid sound and have a melodic hook in the break. Booom...&nbsp;</div>\r\n', '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Rayzers deliver two strong powerful techno tracks in his debut Acid EP on CTS. Ilex is dark and have expressive groove as well as perceptible house music connections in contradistinction to stright tight headline track of the EP which is dedicated to acid sound and have a melodic hook in the break. Booom...&nbsp;</div>\r\n', '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Rayzers deliver two strong powerful techno tracks in his debut Acid EP on CTS. Ilex is dark and have expressive groove as well as perceptible house music connections in contradistinction to stright tight headline track of the EP which is dedicated to acid sound and have a melodic hook in the break. Booom...</div>\r\n', 'Rayzers - Acid<br />\r\nRayzers - Ilex', 1, '2019-07-06 12:08:03', '2019-07-06 12:08:03'),
(1848, 1848, 'Sergio Mega - Back 2 The Future', 'CTS 359193', '2019-06-26', '1848_s.jpg', 'https://www.beatport.com/release/back-2-the-future/2667913', 'https://youtu.be/yavHaTkxaxo', '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Back 2 The Future by Sergio Mega - headline track of the artist album is coming out on CTS. Modern disco sound of the track built on analog synth parts is spiced with sequenced bassline and expressive tom drumfills. Optimistic mood of the tune reinforced with music video. Derisive and sometime absurdistic stile of the video where 3D graphics neighbouring with 8 bit animation allows&nbsp;to show ironic view to some important issues and modern accents of new cosmic era.<br />\r\nRemix by Monovakzin is coming with original mix. Groovy bit dirty vibes and dreamy disco timbres polette of the remix are fills up and completes the EP.</div>\r\n', '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Back 2 The Future от Sergio Mega - заглавный трека одноименного альбома артиста выходит на CTS.&nbsp;Современный диско-саунд трека построенный на партиях аналоговых синтезаторов, приправлен секвенциями баслайна и ярко выраженными диско-ударными.&nbsp;Оптимистичное настроение композиции подкреплено музыкальным видеоклипом. Насмешливый, иногда абсурдистский стиль видео,&nbsp;в котором трехмерная графика соседствует с 8-битной анимацией,&nbsp;позволил продемонстрировать иронический взгляд на некоторые важные темы и современные акценты новой космической эры. Релиз включает ремикс от Monovakzin. Немного dirty грув и палитра дрими-диско тембров ремикса наполняют и завершают ЕР.</div>\r\n', '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Back 2 The Future від Sergio Mega - титульний трек однойменного альбому артиста виходить на CTS.&nbsp;Сучасний disco-саунд треку побудований на партіях аналогових синтезаторів, приправлений&nbsp;секвенціями баслайна і яскраво вираженими disco-ударними. Оптимістичний настрій композиції підкріплено музичним&nbsp;відеокліпом.&nbsp;<br />\r\nНасмішливий, іноді абсурдистський стиль відео, в якому 3D графіка сусідить з 8-бітною анімацією,&nbsp;дозволив продемонструвати іронічний погляд на деякі важливі теми і сучасні акценти нової космічної ери. Реліз включає ремікс від Monovakzin.&nbsp;Трохи dirty грув і палітра Дрім-диско тембрів реміксу наповнюють і завершують ЕР.</div>\r\n', '<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yavHaTkxaxo\">Sergio Mega -&nbsp;Back 2 The Future (Original Mix)</a><br />\r\nSergio Mega -&nbsp;Back 2 The Future (Monovakzin Remix)', 1, '2019-07-26 09:57:16', '2019-07-26 09:57:16');
